20a%20decade%20of%20professional%20experience%20in%20media%2C%20politics%2C%20and%20government%20for%20compelling%20storytelling%20and%20unparalleled%20insight%20into%20the%20news.''%C2%A0He%20described%20himself%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bdestroyer%20of%20stigma%20and%20bureaucratic%20silos%26quot%3B%20and%20a%20%26quot%3Bbeliever%20in%20the%20common%20good.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20described%20himself%20as%20a%20cat%20person%20who%20%26quot%3Bhates%20driving%20cars%2C%20preferring%20to%20bicycle%20or%20ride%20trains.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20data-component-name%3D%5C%22paragraph%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%22cms.cnn.com%2F_components%2Fparagraph%2Finstances%2Fparagraph_02BD2192-FDA0-DAE0-94BE-F1273D3A151F%40published%5C%22%20data-analytics-observe%3D%5C%22off%5C%22%20data-editable%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%20data-article-gutter%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3EIn%202014%20and%202015%2C%20he%20won%20the%20Society%20of%20Professional%20Journalists'%20award%20for%20newspaper%20commentary%20in%20Pennsylvania.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECommissioner%20Vanore%20told%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inquirer.com%2Fcrime%2Fjosh-kruger-killed-point-breeze-shooting-philadelphia-journalist-20231002.html%5C%22%3EThe%20Philadelphia%20Inquirer.%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9CEither%20the%20door%20was%20open%2C%20or%20the%20offender%20knew%20how%20to%20get%20the%20door%20open.%20We%20just%20don't%20know%20yet.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20data-component-name%3D%5C%22paragraph%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%22cms.cnn.com%2F_components%2Fparagraph%2Finstances%2Fparagraph_04B63F09-7442-824E-E3CA-F1273D1EDF8B%40published%5C%22%20data-analytics-observe%3D%5C%22off%5C%22%20data-editable%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%20data-article-gutter%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E''We%20are%20shocked%20and%20saddened%20by%20Josh's%20death.%20Josh%20cared%20deeply%20about%20our%20city%20and%20its%20residents%2C%20which%20was%20evident%20both%20in%20his%20public%20service%20and%20in%20his%20writing%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20mayor.%20%E2%80%9CHis%20intelligence%2C%20creativity%2C%20passion%2C%20and%20wit%20shone%20brightly%20in%20everything%20that%20he%20did%20%E2%80%93%20and%20his%20light%20was%20dimmed%20much%20too%20soon.%20We%20were%20exceedingly%20fortunate%20to%20call%20him%20a%20colleague%20and%20our%20prayers%20are%20with%20everyone%20who%20knew%20and%20loved%20him%2C%C2%A0%20Philadelphia%20Mayor%20Jim%20Kenney%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%3Cem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2023%2F10%2F02%2Fus%2Fjosh-kruger-death-philadelphia%2Findex.html%5C%22%3ECNN.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Committee%20to%20Protect%20Journalists%20also%20released%20a%20statement%20about%20the%20killing.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E''We%20are%20deeply%20disturbed%20by%20the%20killing%20of%20freelance%20journalist%20Josh%20Kruger%20and%20extend%20our%20condolences%20to%20his%20colleagues%20and%20loved%20ones.%20We%20call%20on%20investigators%20to%20thoroughly%20investigate%20his%20killing%20to%20determine%20whether%20the%20attack%20was%20related%20to%20his%20work%2C''%C2%A0Katherine%20Jacobsen%2C%20the%20center's%20U.S.%20and%20Canada%20program%20coordinator.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDistrict%20Attorney%20Larry%20Krasner%20assured%20people%20that%20the%20Philadelphia%20Police%20are%20working%20to%20identify%20the%20person%20behind%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696328700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fldqggo28_josh-kruger_625x300_03_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-journalist-and-activist-josh-kruger-shot-7-times-in-the-chest-dies-police-4445535%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mr.%20Kruger%20worked%20as%20a%20journalist%20and%20covered%20various%20issues%20like%20LGBTQ%2B%20rights%2C%20homelessness%2C%20HIV%2C%20and%20addiction%20in%20publications%20like%20The%20Philadelphia%20Citizen%20and%20The%20Philadelphia%20Inquirer.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl