20according%20to%20an%20excerpt%20from%20Michael%20Lewis'%20new%20book%20on%20FTX%20%26quot%3BGoing%20Infinite%2C%26quot%3B%20published%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fopinions%2Finteractive%2F2023%2Fmichael-lewis-sam-bankman-fried-ftx-crypto%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Washi%3Cu%3Engton%20Post%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Monday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBankman-Fried%20had%20a%20Zoom%20meeting%20with%20Wintour%20on%20Valentine's%20Day%20in%202022%20while%20he%20was%20staying%20at%20the%20Beverly%20Hilton%20hotel%20in%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20per%20the%20excerpt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20crypto%20tycoon%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-bankman-fried-anna-wintour-met-gala-no-idea-2023-10%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%26quot%3Bdidn't%20know%20who%20she%20was%26quot%3B%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20was%20vaguely%20aware%20that%20she%20was%20the%20editor%20of%20a%20magazine%2C%20Lewis%20recounted%20during%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbsnews.com%2Fnews%2Fftx-founder-sam-bankman-fried-michael-lewis-book-60-minutes-transcript%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Einterview%20with%20CBS%20%26quot%3B60%20Minutes%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBankman-Fried%2C%20who%20was%20late%20for%20the%20meeting%2C%20was%20playing%20his%20favourite%20video%20game%20Storybook%20Brawl%20and%20responded%20%26quot%3Byup%26quot%3B%20to%20everything%20Wintour%20was%20saying%20including%20her%20personal%20invitation%20to%20the%20Met%20Gala%20without%20really%20paying%20attention.%20He%20even%20agreed%20to%20Wintour's%20suggestion%20that%20he%20finance%20the%20whole%20event.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWintour%20ended%20the%20conversation%20%26quot%3Bwarmly%2C%26quot%3B%20Lewis%20wrote%20saying%20that%20she%20had%20gotten%20what%20she%20came%20for.%20After%20the%20meeting%20Bankman-Fried%20thought%3A%20%26quot%3B'I%20would%20have%20to%20think%20hard%20if