%20on%20the%20design-side%20and%20execution%20of%20student-loan%20programs.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3ELack%20of%20funding%20for%20Federal%20Student%20Aid%20is%20also%20concerning%20for%20repayment%2C%20Kvaal%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20top%20official%20in%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20Education%20knew%20the%20student-loan%20industry%20was%20broken%20when%20he%20started%20the%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20Secretary%20of%20Education%20James%20Kvaal%20joined%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20administration%20in%202021.%20At%20that%20point%2C%20Americans%20were%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20the%20pandemic%2C%20and%20as%20a%20result%2C%20student-loan%20borrowers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-payment-pause-extended-6-months-supreme-court-2022-11%5C%22%3Ehad%20not%20been%20required%20to%20pay%20their%20bills%20since%20March%202020%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20that%20didn't%20mean%20the%20problems%20in%20the%20industry%20were%20at%20bay%20%E2%80%94%20in%20fact%2C%20that%20was%20far%20from%20the%20reality.%20Student-loan%20borrowers%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstories-of-student-loan-debt-hamster-wheel-borrowers-cant-escape-2022-1%5C%22%3Econtinuing%20to%20struggle%20under%20big%20debt%20burdens%3C%2Fa%3E%20they%20had%20been%20paying%20off%20for%20decades%2C%20and%20minimal%20regulation%20over%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-company-mohela-extensive-servicing-delays-repayment-borrowers-warren-2023-9%5C%22%3Efederal%20loan%20servicers%3C%2Fa%3E%20didn't%20help%20matters.%20Kvaal%20told%20Insider%20that%20he%20viewed%20it%20as%20%26quot%3Ban%20untested%20experiment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20had%20people%20taking%20out%20more%20loans%20than%20they%20ever%20had%20before%2C%26quot%3B%20Kvaal%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20no%20previous%20generation%20had%20gone%20through%20something%20like%20this.%20At%20the%20department%2C%20obviously%2C%20we%20were%20in%20the%20student-loan%20pause%2C%20but%20the%20pause%20was%20papering%20over%20some%20fundamental%20problems.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20over%20three%20years%2C%20the%20student-loan%20payment%20pause%20has%20ended%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-payment-pause-is-over-interest-resuming-borrower-balances-2023-8%5C%22%3Einterest%20started%20accruing%20again%20on%20September%201%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20bills%20are%20now%20starting%20to%20become%20due.%20Kvaal%20said%20that%20prior%20to%20the%20pause%2C%20millions%20of%20borrowers%20were%20defaulting%20on%20their%20loans%2C%20a%20tiny%20percentage%20of%20borrowers%20received%20relief%20through%20Public%20Service%20Loan%20Forgiveness%2C%20and%20borrowers%20with%20disabilities%C2%A0continued%20to%20see%20their%20benefits%20garnished%20even%20though%20they%20qualified%20for%20relief%20%E2%80%94%20things%20he%20said%20were%20all%20a%20result%20of%20%26quot%3Bdeep-rooted%20structural%20problems%20in%20the%20loan%20programs%20on%20the%20policy%20design%2C%20but%20also%20on%20the%20execution%20side.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20really%20only%20in%20the%20last%C2%A010%20or%2015%20years%2C%20as%20we%20started%20to%20look%20more%20closely%20at%20how%20many%20borrowers%20are%20struggling%2C%20that%20we've%20realized%20there's%20something%20really%20wrong%20with%20this%20system%2C%26quot%3B%20Kvaal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20that's%20the%20case%2C%20why%20are%20those%20issues%20taking%20so%20long%20to%20fix%3F%20Kvaal%20pointed%20to%20limited%20resources%20the%20Education%20Department%20has%20to%20give%20to%20federal%20student-loan%20servicers%2C%20which%20he%20said%20has%20contributed%20to%20mismanagement%20over%20the%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EOngoing%20challenges%20with%20borrowers%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBorrowers%20need%20the%20industry%20to%20be%20functioning%20smoothly%20now%20more%20than%20ever%20with%20the%20transition%20back%20into%20repayment.%C2%A0Some%20have%20told%20Insider%20they%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-borrowers-cant-reach-company-mohela-pslf-debt-relief-2022-10%5C%22%3Espent%20hours%20on%20the%20phone%20waiting%20for%20answers%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20their%20customer%20service%20representative%20to%20no%20avail%2C%20and%20others%20have%20received%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-payments-resume-confusion-borrowers-debt-relief-biden-2023-8%5C%22%3Einaccurate%20billing%20statements%3C%2Fa%3E%20they%20have%20struggled%20to%20get%20fixed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKvaal%20said%20he's%20aware%20of%20the%20challenges%20borrowers%20have%20had%20as%20they%20geared%20up%20for%20repayment%2C%20acknowledging%20that%20%26quot%3Bstudent-loan%20programs%20are%20very%2C%20very%20complicated%2C%20and%20the%20servicers%20do%20not%20have%20the%20funding%20that%20we%20would%20like%20to%20give%20them%20to%20better%20serve%20borrowers.%26quot%3B%20While%20that%20might%20be%20the%20case%2C%20he%20said%20his%20department%20is%20working%20to%20strengthen%20accountability%20over%20servicers%20through%20new%20contracts%20that%20will%20go%20into%20effect%20in%20the%20spring.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20lawmakers%20want%20that%20process%20to%20move%20faster.%20Massachusetts%20Sen.%20Elizabeth%20Warren%2C%20for%20example%2C%20joined%20some%20of%20her%20Democratic%20colleagues%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felizabeth-warren-student-loan-companies-bad-customer-service-borrowers-repayment-2023-9%5C%22%3Erequesting%20information%20from%20four%20major%20federal%20servicers%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20second%20time%20this%20year%20on%20their%20preparedness%20to%20help%20borrowers%20with%20repayment.%C2%A0When%20Warren%20first%20asked%20in%20July%2C%20the%20servicers'%20responses%20left%20her%20%26quot%3Bdeeply%20worried%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20some%20of%20them%20anticipated%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bus