%2C%20The%20Wire%20etc.%2C%20and%20most%20recently%20the%20journalists%20of%20NewsClick.%20The%20BJP%20government%20has%20also%20tried%20to%20convert%20the%20media%20into%20a%20mouthpiece%20for%20its%20partisan%20and%20ideological%20interests%20by%20facilitating%20the%20takeover%20of%20media%20organisations%20by%20crony%20capitalists.%20Both%20the%20government%20and%20its%20ideologically%20aligned%20organisations%20have%20resorted%20to%20reprisals%20against%20individual%20journalists%20who%20spoke%20truth%20to%20power.%20Furthermore%2C%20the%20BJP%20government%20has%20also%20spearheaded%20regressive%20policies%20like%20the%20Information%20Technology%20Rules%202021%20that%20constrict%20the%20media%20from%20reporting%20objectively.%20In%20doing%20so%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20not%20only%20hiding%20its%20sins%20of%20omission%20and%20commission%20from%20the%20people%20of%20India.%20It%20is%20also%20compromising%20India%E2%80%99s%20global%20standing%20as%20a%20mature%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20government%E2%80%99s%20coercive%20actions%20are%20invariably%20directed%20against%20only%20those%20media%20organisations%20and%20journalists%20that%20speak%20truth%20to%20power.%20Ironically%2C%20the%20BJP%20government%20is%20paralysed%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20taking%20action%20against%20those%20journalists%20inciting%20hatred%20and%20divisiveness%20in%20the%20nation.%20In%20the%20national%20interest%2C%20it%20would%20behove%20the%20BJP%20Government%20to%20focus%20on%20genuine%20issues%20of%20concern%20to%20the%20nation%20and%20the%20people%2C%20and%20stop%20attacking%20the%20media%20to%20distract%20attention%20from%20its%20failures.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJai%20Hind.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696326888000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2F10154711%2FUntitled-design-2021-02-10T154651.122.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ffresh-attack-media-india-parties-condemn-raids-newsclick%22%