%20Sergey%20Sobyanin%2C%20the%20Dossier%20Center%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20most%20of%20the%20list%20covered%20the%20addresses%20of%20public%20institutions%20like%20metro%20stations%2C%20police%20headquarters%2C%20and%20hospitals%2C%20it%20also%20pinpointed%20secret%20locations%20like%20an%20ammunition%20depot%20in%20Leningrad%20and%20undercover%20facilities%20run%20by%20the%20Federal%20Protective%20Service%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Dossier%20Center.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20case%2C%20the%20document%20even%20included%20the%20apartment%20numbers%20of%20two%20homes%20used%20by%20spies%20in%20Moscow%2C%20the%20Dossier%20Center%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20list%20of%20residential%20addresses%20also%20revealed%20at%20least%20six%20apartment%20buildings%20in%20Moscow%20that%20contain%20homes%20sold%20or%20given%20to%20intelligence%20officers%20in%20the%20Foreign%20Intelligence%20Service%2C%20Russia's%20top%20external%20intelligence%20agency%2C%20per%20the%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%2010%20other%20entries%20in%20the%20document%20listed%20buildings%20in%20Moscow%20used%20by%20agents%20of%20the%20Federal%20Security%20Service%2C%20Russia's%20internal%20security%20and%20counterintelligence%20agency%2C%20per%20the%20Dossier%20Center.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFurther%20entries%20also%20revealed%20dozens%20of%20undercover%20offices%20and%20facilities%20used%20by%20the%20Federal%20Protective%20Service%2C%20which%20is%20responsible%20for%20guarding%20Russia's%20top%20leaders%2C%20and%20the%20Federal%20Security%20Service%2C%20the%20outlet%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20these%20locations%20have%20already%20been%20identified%20as%20Russian%20intelligence%20facilities%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheins.ru%2Fpolitika%2F237705%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einvestigative%20outlets%20such%20as%20Bellingcat%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Dossier%20Center%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFacilities%20and%20safe%20houses%20in%20the%20Primorsky%2C%20Leningrad%2C%20St.%20Petersburg%2C%20and%20Bryansk%20regions%20were%20also%20on%20the%20list%2C%20the%20Dossier%20Center%20wrote%2C%20showing%20screenshots%20of%20the%20document.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20Kremlin%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20sent%20outside%20regular%20business%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-accidentally-doxes-own-spies-secret-bases-dossier-center-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696324327000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F651bd142617692f0d03d4595%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-accidentally-doxes-own-spies-secret-bases-dossier-center-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20434-page%20document%20was%20supposed%20to%20inform%20power%20suppliers%20which%20buildings%20should%20not%20lose%20power%20during%20a%20blackout%2C%20the%20Dossier%20Center%20reported.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mloh%40insider.com%20(Matthew%20Loh)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-accidentally-doxes-own-spies-secret-bases-dossier-center-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20resell%20tickets%20online%20and%20make%20up%20to%20%2432%2C000%20in%20profit%20a%20month.%20Here's%20how%20I%20do%20it.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221757%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22headshot%20of%20Shiraz%20Mawani%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F651aea90ecc9f4001942a2b5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221318%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EShiraz%20Mawani.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Shiraz%20Mawani%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EShiraz%20Mawani%20is%20an%20accounting%20manager%20with%20a%20ticket-reselling%20side%20hustle%20and%20YouTube%20channel.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAfter%20selling%20a%20few%20tickets%20to%20make%20a%20hockey%20game%20more%20affordable%20in%202014%2C%20he%20continued%20to%20resell.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENow%20he%20resells%20hundreds%20of%20sporting%20and%20concert%20tickets%20and%20brings%20in%20six%20figures%20in%20sales%20monthly.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Shiraz%20Mawani%2C%20an%20accounting%20manager%2C%20ticket%20reseller%2C%20and%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2F%40thumbsuprun%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3EYouTuber%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20in%20Toronto.%20Insider%20has%20verified%20his%20earnings%20with%20documentation.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20fell%20into%20ticket%20reselling%20in%202014.%20My%20friends%20and%20I%20used%20to%20go%20to%20an%20NHL%20playoff%20game%20every%20year.%20That%20year%2C%20the%20ticket%20prices%20were%20too%20high%2C%20so%20we%20decided%20to%20buy%20extra%20tickets%2C%20sell%20them%20for%20a%20higher%20price%20than%20we%20paid%2C%20and%20use%20the%20profits%20from%20the%20tickets%20to%20attend%20the%20game%20for%20a%20lower%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20sold%20a%20couple%20of%20the%20tickets%20through%20Craigslist%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kijiji.ca%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EKijiji%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20Canadian%20selling%20platform%2C%20and%20then%20decided%20to%20try%20to%20sell%20two%20tickets%20through%20StubHub%20%E2%80%94%20my%20first%20time%20using%20the%20platform.%20I%20didn't%20know%20much%20about%20it%2C%20and%20at%20the%20time%2C%20I%20didn't%20imagine%20that%20anyone%20would%20buy%20tickets%20online%20without%20any%20idea%20who%20the%20seller%20was.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20posting%20the%20tickets%2C%20I%20was%20sitting%20at%20a%20restaurant%20with%20some%20friends%2C%20and%20I%20got%20an%20email%20saying%20that%20someone%20had%20bought%20them.%20We%20used%20the%20profits%20from%20reselling%20tickets%20to%20pay%20half%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20normal-price%20tickets%2C%20and%20my%20friends%20and%20I%20got%20to%20go%20to%20the%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENine%20years%20later%2C%20I%20still%20resell%20tickets%20in%20addition%20to%20my%20full-time%20job%20as%20an%20accounting%20manager.%20I%20make%20up%20to%20%2432%2C000%20a%20month%20in%20profit.%20Here's%20how%20I%20do%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFirst%2C%20I%20expanded%20into%20concerts%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20months%20after%20the%20NHL%20playoff%20game%2C%20one%20of%20my%20friends%20told%20me%20that%20Bruno%20Mars%20and%20Katy%20Perry%20were%20coming%20to%20Toronto.%20They%20wanted%20to%20try%20to%20sell%20tickets%20the%20same%20way%20that%20we%20had%20for%20the%20NHL%20game%20%E2%80%94%20except%20this%20time%2C%20we%20weren't%20interested%20in%20attending%20the%20event%20ourselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20continued%20reselling%20tickets%20to%20local%20events.%20After%20a%20while%2C%20my%20friend%20lost%20interest%2C%20but%20I%20continued%20to%20run%20with%20it.%20I%20was%20constantly%20looking%20for%20tickets%20going%20on%20sale%20in%20Toronto%2C%20and%20eventually%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2065%25%20of%20the%20tickets%20that%20I%20resell%20are%20to%20sporting%20events%2C%20while%2035%25%20are%20events%20including%20concerts%2C%20Broadway%20shows%2C%20and%20comedy%20events.%20That's%20just%20a%20personal%20preference%20because%20I'm%20not%20a%20big%20music%20person.%20Sports%20are%20what%20I%20know%20and%20where%20my%20focus%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThere%20are%202%20sides%20to%20ticket%20reselling%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20people%20looking%20to%20sell%20a%20few%20tickets%2C%20and%20then%20there%20are%20ticket%20brokers%20looking%20to%20make%20a%20profit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDepending%20on%20which%20type%20of%20seller%20you%20are%2C%20there%20are%20different%20tools%20you%20have%20access%20to%20on%20each%20platform.%20The%20average%20seller%20sees%20only%20one%20side%20of%20the%20platform.%20Ticket%20brokers%2C%20though%2C%20have%20access%20to%20tools%20that%20identify%20which%20tickets%20are%20going%20on%20sale%2C%20a%20different%20rate%20structure%2C%20and%20a%20different%20suite%20of%20software.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20ticket%20broker%2C%20I%20use%20a%20point-of-sale%20system%20that%20uses%20an%20application%20programming%20interface%20to%20allow%20me%20to%20list%20tickets%20on%20multiple%20platforms%20at%20once.%20I'll%20list%20my%20inventory%20on%20my%20POS%20system%2C%20which%20I%20access%20for%20free%2C%20and%20it'll%20put%20the%20tickets%20on%20selling%20platforms%20such%20as%20StubHub%20using%20the%20API.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20favorite%20selling%20platform%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tickpick.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ETickPick%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20I%20find%20that%20it%20has%20the%20best%20pricing%20for%20purchasing%2C%20and%20its%20customer%20service%20is%20excellent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20there%20are%20tickets%20that%20expire%20or%20go%20unsold%20before%20events%2C%20I'll%20drop%20the%20prices%2C%20but%20there's%20always%20a%20limit%20to%20how%20low%20I'll%20go%20before%20I%20simply%20let%20the%20tickets%20sit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPricing%20depends%20on%20each%20seller%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20know%20many%20sellers%20who%20try%20to%20price%20their%20tickets%20for%20as%20cheap%20as%20possible.%20I%20wouldn't%20say%20that%20that's%20the%20wrong%20strategy%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20how%20I%20do%20ticket%20pricing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20there's%20a%20high%20search%20volume%20for%20an%20event%20or%20an%20artist%20with%20a%20strong%20social%20following%2C%20or%20they're%20going%20to%20a%20major%20city%20or%20specific%20venue%2C%20I%20may%20price%20the%20tickets%20more%20aggressively.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20every%20ticket%20is%20priced%20differently%2C%20my%20general%20goal%20is%20to%20earn%20between%20a%2030%25%20and%2040%25%20profit%20margin.%20With%20my%20type%20of%20inventory%2C%20I'm%20normally%20closer%20to%2030%25%20after%20my%20sell-through%20fees%20are%20taken%20into%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFor%20sales%20that%20take%20place%20on%20online%20marketplaces%2C%20there's%20no%20price%20negotiation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20have%20individual%20buyers%20approach%20me%2C%20I'll%20try%20to%20offer%20them%20a%20fair%20price%20below%20the%20market%20value%20and%20may%20allow%20for%20small%20negotiations%2C%20but%20I%20generally%20keep%20firm%20on%20pricing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20May%2C%20I%20sold%20850%20tickets%20for%20just%20under%20%24121%2C000%20in%20sales%2C%20which%20equaled%20about%20%2432%2C000%20in%20profit%2C%20but%20this%20number%20ranges%20from%20month%20to%20month%20depending%20on%20the%20season.%20This%20year%20has%20been%20very%20positive%20for%20me%2C%20and%20I'm%20running%20about%20a%20%2430%2C000-a-month%20profit%20on%20average.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20started%20a%20YouTube%20channel%20in%202018%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20first%20YouTube%20videos%20were%20vlogs%20of%20me%20delivering%20tickets%20to%20will%20call%20locations%20in%20different%20cities%20so%20buyers%20could%20pick%20them%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20I%20returned%20from%20these%20trips%2C%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20had%20a%20bit%20of%20knowledge%20that%20I%20could%20share%20with%20other%20people%20looking%20to%20resell%20tickets%2C%20so%20I%20started%20creating%20content%20about%20helping%20the%20average%20fan%20sell%20their%20tickets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMostly%2C%20people%20ask%20me%20what%20to%20do%20with%20their%20tickets%20if%20an%20event%20has%20been%20canceled%2C%20about%20timing%20for%20reselling%20tickets%2C%20and%20whether%20they%20can%20trust%20specific%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20spend%20between%2020%20and%2040%20hours%20a%20week%20working%20on%20my%20resale%20business%2C%20so%20it%20could%20be%20a%20full-time%20gig%20if%20I%20wanted%20it%20to%20be%2C%20but%20at%20this%20point%2C%20I%20consider%20ticket%20resale%20and%20my%20YouTube%20channel%20to%20be%20side%20hustles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-reselling-tickets-earns-me-tens-of-thousands-per-month-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696324021000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F651aeaa2ecc9f4001942a2cb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-reselling-tickets-earns-me-tens-of-thousands-per-month-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shiraz%20Mawani%20resells%20tickets%20online%20and%20makes%20up%20to%20%2432%2C000%20a%20month.%20It%20started%20as%20a%20way%20to%20cut%20down%20the%20cost%20of%20seeing%20a%20hockey%20game%20with%20his%20friends%20in%202014.%20Now%2C%20reselling%20is%20his%20side%20hustle.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sweilbaker3%40gmail.com%20(Sasha%20Weilbaker)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-reselling-tickets-earns-me-tens-of-thousands-per-month-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UAE%20holds%20major%20oil%20and%20gas%20conference%20ahead%20of%20hosting%20UN%20climate%20talks%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696323975000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104128449%2Cimgsize-1801904.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fuae-holds-major-oil-and-gas-conference-just-ahead-of-hosting-un-climate-talks-in-dubai%2Farticleshow%2F104128097.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F104128097.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20president-designate%20of%20the%20upcomi