3.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BUsed%20To%20Have%20Blackouts%20Due%20To%20Low-Salt%20Diet%26quot%3B%3A%20Boney%20On%20Sridevi's%20Death%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EProducer%20Boney%20Kapoor%20has%20finally%20opened%20up%20about%20his%20wife%2C%20superstar%20Sridevi's%20tragic%20demise.%20Sridevi%20died%20in%20her%20hotel%20room%20in%20Dubai%20due%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsridevis-body-to-brought-back-to-mumbai-from-dubai-today-for-last-rites-updates-1817119%23%3A~%3Atext%3DSridevi%252C%252054%252C%2520died%2520in%2520her%2Cno%2520history%2520of%2520heart%2520ailment.%5C%22%3Eaccidental%20drowning%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20on%20February%2024%2C%202018.%20She%20was%2054.%20Now%2C%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fsi%3D4rf5zgOvi6ldBhNm%26v%3DZDjAxOdCPEM%26feature%3Dyoutu.be%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Boney%20Kapoor%20mentioned%20that%20Sridevi%20used%20to%20follow%20a%20strict%20diet.%20The%20producer%20also%20spoke%20about%20the%20interrogation%20and%20the%20lie-detector%20test%20he%20had%20to%20go%20through%20after%20Sridevi's%20death.%20Boney%20Kapoor%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20not%20a%20natural%20death%2C%20it%20was%20an%20accidental%20death.%20I%20thought%20I%20would%20never%20speak%20about%20it%20because%20I%20spoke%20about%20it%20for%20almost%2024-48%20hours%20together%2C%20when%20I%20was%20being%20investigated%2C%20and%20interrogated%20and%20that%20is%20how%20I%20got%20a%20clean%20chit%20from%20the%20Dubai%20police.%20In%20Fact%2C%20the%20officer%20said%20that%20we%20had%20to%20do%20this%2C%20we%20had%20to%20go%20through%20this%20because%20there%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20pressure%20from%20the%20Indian%20media.%20They%20discovered%20there%20was%20no%20foul%20play.%20I%20went%20through%20all%20the%20interrogation%2C%20including%20the%20lie%20detector.%20The%20report%20which%20came%20clearly%20stated%20that%20it%20was%20an%20accidental%20death%20by%20drowning.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBoney%20Kapoor%20also%20mentioned%20how%20Sridevi%20used%20to%20experience%20blackouts%20due%20to%20her%20no-salt%20diet.%20Even%20though%20the%20doctor%20had%20advised%20Sridevi%20to%20avoid%20a%20severe%20low-salt%20diet%20due%20to%20her%20low%20blood%20pressure%2C%20the%20actress%2C%20at%20the%20time%20of%20her%20death%2C%20was%20swearing%20by%20one%20of%20the%20same%20routines.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBoney%20Kapoor%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20family%20physician%20always%20used%20to%20tell%20Sri%20(Sridevi)%20whenever%20you%20diet%2C%20because%20whenever%20she%20used%20to%20start%20a%20new%20film%2C%20she%20used%20to%20want%20to%20look%20good%20because%20the%20fact%20is%20what%20you%20are%20in%20real%20life%2C%20on%E2%80%93screen%20especially%20for%20cinemascope%20you%20will%20look%20broader.%20She%20wanted%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20she%20is%20chiselled%2C%20in%20good%20shape%20so%20that%20on%20screen%20she%20also%20looks%20like%20it.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20continued%2C%20%E2%80%9CSince%20the%20time%20she%20was%20married%20to%20me%2C%20she%20has%20had%20blackouts%20on%20a%20couple%20of%20occasions.%20The%20doctor%20kept%20on%20telling%20her%20that%20you%20have%20a%20low%20bp%20issue%2C%20don't%20stick%20to%20a%20severe%20diet%20where%20you%20avoid%20salt.%20Because%20most%20of%20the%20females%20believe%20that%20salt%20creates%20water%20retention%20that's%20why%20your%20face%20is%20puffy.%20That%C2%A0%20is%20one%20reason%20why%20Sri%20used%20to%20avoid%20salt.%20We%20used%20to%20tell%20her%20that%20even%20if%20you%20are%20having%20some%20salad%2C%20just%20sprinkle%20some%20salt%20on%20it.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBoney%20Kapoor%20also%20recalled%20his%20conversation%20with%20south%20superstar%20Nagarjuna%20after%20Sridevi's%20death.%20He%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CLater%2C%20when%20she%20passed%20away%20Nagarjuna%20had%20come%20home%20to%20offer%20his%20condolences.%20He%20told%20me%20that%20during%20one%20of%20his%20shootings%2C%20she%20was%20again%20on%20a%20crash%20diet%20and%20how%20she%20fell%20in%20the%20bathroom%20and%20broke%20her%20teeth.%20I%20knew%20she%20had%20broken%20teeth%20and%20had%20those%20artificial%20casps.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20I%20got%20married%20to%20her%20I%20knew%20she%20has%20this%20tendency%20of%20going%20on%20a%20strict%20diet%2C%20I%20used%20to%20push%20my%20daughters%20to%20tell%20her%20that%20she%20must%20have%20some%20salt.%20I%20used%20to%20push%20her%20myself.%20Whenever%20we%20used%20to%20go%20out%20for%20dinner%2C%20she%20used%20to%20say%2C%20%E2%80%98food%20with%20no%20salt.'%20Unfortunately%2C%20she%20didn't%20take%20this%20seriously%2C%20and%20he%20also%20thought%20maybe%20it%20can't%20be%20this%20serious%20until%20the%20incident%20happened%2C%E2%80%9D%20Boney%20Kapoor%20finished%20off.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESridevi%20and%20Boney%20Kapoor%20got%20married%20in%201996.%20They%20welcomed%20their%20first%20daughter%2C%20Janhvi%20Kapoor%20in%201997%2C%20and%20Khushi%20Kapoor%20in%20November%202000.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696318860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fhgigj5u_boney_625x300_03_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fboney-kapoor-on-sridevi-s-tragic-death-went-through-interrogation-lie-detector-test-4444657%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sridevi%20died%20in%20her%20hotel%20room%20in%20Dubai%20due%20to%20accidental%20drowning%2C%20on%20February%2024%2C%202018%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fboney-kapoor-on-sridevi-s-tragic-death-went-through-interrogation-lie-detector-test-4444657%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fboney-kapoor-on-sridevi-s-tragic-death-went-through-interrogation-lie-detector-test-4444657%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fboney-kapoor-on-sridevi-s-tragic-death-went-through-interrogation-lie-detector-test-4444657%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3B2%20Crore%20Party%20Workers'%20Sentiments%26quot%3B%3A%20EPS%20Says%20AIADMK-BJP%20Break-Up%20%26quot%3BFinal%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20first%20public%20remarks%20after%20the%20All%20India%20Anna%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%20(AIADMK)%20pulled%20the%20plug%20on%20its%20alliance%20with%20BJP%2C%20party%20chief%20Edappadi%20K%20Palaniswami%20has%20said%20the%20decision%20was%20%26quot%3Bfinal%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20it%20was%20not%20his%20decision%20alone%2C%20but%20that%20of%20two%20crore%20party%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20media%20last%20night%2C%20Mr%20Palaniswami%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BTwo%20crore%20party%20workers%20shared%20their%20sentiments%20in%20a%20consultative%20meeting.%20It%20was%20on%20that%20basis%20that%20AIADMK%20took%20the%20decision%20to%20exit%20the%20NDA.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20my%20decision%20as%20the%20party's%20general%20secretary.%20This%20is%20a%20decision%20of%20the%20AIADMK%20cadre.%20When%20a%20resolution%20is%20adopted%2C%20that%20is%20final%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20On%20what%20led%20to%20the%20break-up%2C%20the%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20were%20forced%20to%20support%20issues%20we%20don't%20agree%20due%20to%20alliance%20dharma.%20Now%20we%20face%20no%20such%20situation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20what%20is%20on%20AIADMK's%20priority%20list%20for%20the%202024%20general%20election%2C%20Mr%20Palaniswami%20said%20the%20focus%20is%20to%20fight%20for%20the%20rights%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20few%20people%20are%20asking%20who%20is%20our%20Prime%20Minister%20candidate.%20In%202019%2C%20did%20Odisha%20CM%2C%20West%20Bengal%20CM%2C%20Kerala%2C%20Telangana%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20did%20they%20face%20election%20by%20projecting%20their%20PM%20candidates%3F%20The%20way%20they%20faced%20elections%20to%20protect%20the%20state's%20rights%2C%20AIADMK%20will%20also%20protect%20Tamil%20Nadu%20people's%20rights.%20We%20will%20meet%20people%20and%20will%20ask%20for%20their%20votes.%20People%20are%20our%20masters%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20AIADMK%20leader%20said%20the%20party%20will%20raise%20the%20voice%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20people%20in%20Parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20won%20on%20the%20votes%20of%20people%20from%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20In%20Parliament%2C%20we%20will%20be%20their%20voice.%20This%20is%20our%20ideology.%20In%20some%20way%2C%20if%20minority%20communities%20like%20Muslims%20and%20Christians%20face%20any%20problem%2C%20AIADMK%20will%20be%20the%20party%20that%20will%20give%20voice%20to%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Palaniswami%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20AIADMK%20last%20month%20ended%20its%20alliance%20with%20BJP%20amid%20a%20face-off%20over%20remarks%20by%20state%20BJP%20president%20K%20Annamalai.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20political%20storm%20over%20DMK%20leader%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin's%20remarks%20on%20Sanatana%20Dharma%2C%20Mr%20Annamalai%20had%20said%20former%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20late%20CN%20Annadurai%2C%20had%20insulted%20Hinduism%20back%20in%201956%20and%20had%20to%20apologise%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20sparked%20a%20huge%20face-off%20with%20AIADMK.%20CN%20Annadurai%20was%20the%20political%20mentor%20of%20AIADMK%20founder%20and%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20MG%20Ramachandran%20and%20is%20a%20revered%20figure%20in%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAIADMK%20demanded%20that%20the%20state%20BJP%20chief%20apologise%20for%20his%20remarks.%20Mr%20Annamalai%2C%20whose%20statements%20have%20been%20seen%20as%20an%20attempt%20to%20carve%20a%20distinct%20political%20identity%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%20refused.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20meeting%20organised%20as%20a%20last-ditch%20attempt%20to%20save%20the%20tie-up%20did%20not%20yield%20desired%20results%2C%20as%20both%20sides%20remained%20adamant%20on%20their%20stand.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Palaniswami's%20latest%20remarks%20have%20put%20to%20rest%20any%20speculation%20about%20the%20possibility%20of%20revival%20of%20ties%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20AIADMK%20had%20suffered%20successive%20defeats%20in%20all%20elections%20it%20fought%20in%20alliance%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20including%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20state%20polls%20the%20same%20year.%20Strains%20in%20the%20alliance%20were%20evident%20when%20the%20leaders%20of%20the%20two%20parties%20did%20not%20campaign%20together%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20bypoll%20in%20Erode%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20AIADMK's%20big%20decision%20on%20its%20alliance%20with%20BJP%20also%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20when%20Mr%20Palaniswami%20has%20consolidated%20his%20position%20as%20the%20top%20leader%20of%20the%20party%2C%20six%20years%20after%20the%20death%20of%20former%20chief%20Minister%20and%20party%20supremo%20J%20Jayalalithaa.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EO%20Panneerselvam%2C%20with%20whom%20Mr%20Palaniswami%20had%20shared%20the%20party's%20leadership%2C%20was%20expelled%20last%20year%20for%20anti-party%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETherefore%2C%20the%202024%20polls%20would%20be%20an%20acid%20test%20for%20Mr%20Palaniswami's%20leadership%20and%20his%20decision%20to%20part%20ways%20with%20the%20BJP%20needs%20to%20be%20seen%20against%20this%20backdrop%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696318800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-07%2Fle67n95_edappadi-k-palaniswami_650x400_11_July_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faiadmk-bjp-e-palaniswami-k-annamalai-adoption-of-a-resolution-is-final-aiadmk-chief-on-ending-bjp-alliance-4444862%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20his%20first%20public%20remarks%20after%20the%20All%20India%20Anna%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%20(AIADMK)%20pulled%20the%20plug%20on%20its%20alliance%20with%20BJP%2C%20party%20chief%20Edappadi%20K%20Palaniswami%20has%20said%20the%20decision%20was%20%26quot%3Bfinal%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faiadmk-bjp-e-palaniswami-k-annamalai-adoption-of-a-resolution-is-final-aiadmk-chief-on-ending-bjp-alliance-4444862%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faiadmk-bjp-e-palaniswami-k-annamalai-adoption-of-a-resolution-is-final-aiadmk-chief-on-ending-bjp-alliance-4444862%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faiadmk-bjp-e-palaniswami-k-annamalai-adoption-of-a-resolution-is-final-aiadmk-chief-on-ending-bjp-alliance-4444862%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BThey're%20Just%20Meat%26quot%3B%3A%20Russia%20Deploys%20Punishment%20Battalions%20To%20Frontlines%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDrunk%20recruits.%20Insubordinate%20soldiers.%20Convicts.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey're%20among%20hundreds%20of%20military%20and%20civilian%20offenders%20who've%20been%20pressed%20into%20Russian%20penal%20units%20known%20as%20%26quot%3BStorm-Z%26quot%3B%20squads%20and%20sent%20to%20the%20frontlines%20in%20Ukraine%20this%20year%2C%20according%20to%2013%20people%20with%20knowledge%20of%20the%20matter%2C%20including%20five%20fighters%20in%20the%20units.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFew%20live%20to%20tell%20their%20tale%2C%20the%20people%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStorm%20fighters%2C%20they're%20just%20meat%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20one%20regular%20soldier%20from%20army%20unit%20no.%2040318%20who%20was%20deployed%20near%20the%20fiercely%20contested%20city%20of%20Bakhmut%20in%20eastern%20Ukraine%20in%20May%20and%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he'd%20given%20medical%20treatment%20to%20a%20group%20of%20six%20or%20seven%20wounded%20Storm-Z%20fighters%20on%20the%20battlefield%2C%20disobeying%20an%20order%20from%20a%20commander%20-%20whose%20name%20he%20didn't%20know%20-%20to%20leave%20the%20men.%20He%20said%20he%20didn't%20know%20why%20the%20commander%20gave%20the%20order%2C%20but%20claimed%20that%20it%20typified%20how%20Storm-Z%20fighters%20were%20considered%20of%20lesser%20value%20than%20ordinary%20troops%20by%20officers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20soldier%2C%20who%20requested%20anonymity%20because%20he%20feared%20prosecution%20in%20Russia%20for%20publicly%20discussing%20the%20war%2C%20said%20he%20had%20sympathy%20for%20the%20men's%20plight%3A%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20commandants%20catch%20anyone%20with%20the%20smell%20of%20alcohol%20on%20their%20breath%2C%20then%20they%20immediately%20send%20them%20to%20the%20Storm%20squads.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20contacted%20by%20Reuters%2C%20an%20officer%20at%20unit%20no.%2040318%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20Storm-Z%20and%20ended%20the%20call.%20The%20Kremlin%20referred%20Reuters%20questions%20to%20the%20Russian%20defence%20ministry%2C%20which%20didn't%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERussian%20state-controlled%20media%20has%20reported%20that%20Storm-Z%20squads%20exist%2C%20that%20they%20took%20part%20in%20intense%20battles%20and%20some%20of%20their%20members%20received%20medals%20for%20bravery%2C%20but%20it%20has%20not%20disclosed%20how%20they%20are%20formed%2C%20or%20the%20losses%20they%20take.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EReuters%20is%20the%20first%20news%20organisation%20to%20compile%20a%20comprehensive%20account%20of%20how%20the%20squads%20are%20put%20together%20and%20deployed%2C%20by%20speaking%20to%20multiple%20sources%20with%20direct%20knowledge%20of%20what%20is%20happening.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELike%20the%20soldier%20from%20unit%20no.%2040318%2C%20the%2013%20people%20interviewed%20-%20who%20also%20include%20four%20relatives%20of%20Storm-Z%20members%20as%20well%20as%20three%20soldiers%20in%20regular%20units%20who%20interacted%20with%20the%20squads%20-%20all%20requested%20anonymity%2C%20citing%20fear%20of%20reprisals.%20Reuters%20verified%20the%20identities%20of%20all%20the%20fighters%20involved%20using%20criminal%20records%2C%20social%20media%20accounts%2C%20or%20by%20speaking%20to%20their%20fellow%20serviceman%20and%20their%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20penal%20squads%2C%20each%20about%20100-150%20strong%20and%20embedded%20within%20regular%20army%20units%2C%20have%20typically%20been%20sent%20to%20the%20most%20exposed%20parts%20of%20the%20front%20and%20often%20sustain%20heavy%20losses%2C%20according%20to%20Reuters%20interviews%20with%20the%20people%2C%20who%20identified%20at%20least%20five%20Storm-Z%20teams%20fighting%20to%20repel%20a%20Ukrainian%20counteroffensive%20in%20the%20east%20and%20south.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThree%20of%20the%20five%20Storm-Z%20fighters%20interviewed%20by%20Reuters%2C%20and%20the%20relatives%20of%20three%20other%20Storm-Z%20fighters%2C%20described%20nightmarish%20engagements%20that%20saw%20much%20of%20their%20squads%20wiped%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20fighter%2C%20with%20a%20conviction%20for%20theft%20who%20was%20recruited%20from%20prison%2C%20said%20all%20but%2015%20of%20the%20120%20men%20in%20his%20unit%20embedded%20with%20the%20237th%20regiment%20were%20killed%20or%20wounded%20in%20fighting%20near%20Bakhmut%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20deployment%20of%20such%20squads%20marks%20a%20departure%20for%20Russia%20in%20Ukraine%3A%20while%20the%20Wagner%20mercenary%20group%20-%20now%20being%20disbanded%20after%20a%20June%20mutiny%20-%20sent%20convicts%20to%20fight%20on%20the%20frontline%2C%20the%20Storm-Z%20units%20come%20under%20the%20direct%20command%20of%20the%20defence%20ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20squads%20also%20combine%20convicts%20who%20volunteer%20to%20fight%20in%20exchange%20for%20the%20promise%20of%20a%20pardon%20with%20regular%20soldiers%20being%20punished%20for%20disciplinary%20breaches%2C%20the%20people%20interviewed%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Storm-Z%20squads%20are%20useful%20to%20the%20Russian%20defence%20ministry%20because%20they%20can%20be%20deployed%20as%20expendable%20infantry%2C%20according%20to%20Conflict%20Intelligence%20Team%2C%20an%20independent%20organisation%20that's%20tracking%20the%20war.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Storm%20fighters%20are%20just%20sent%20to%20the%20most%20dangerous%20parts%20of%20the%20front%2C%20in%20defence%20and%20in%20attack%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20group%2C%20which%20was%20founded%20in%20Russia%2C%20told%20Reuters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Russian%20defence%20ministry%20has%20never%20acknowledged%20creating%20Storm-Z%20units%2C%20the%20first%20reports%20of%20their%20existence%20emerged%20in%20April%20when%20the%20Institute%20for%20the%20Study%20of%20War%2C%20a%20U.S.-based%20think-tank%2C%20cited%20what%20it%20said%20appeared%20to%20be%20a%20leaked%20Russian%20military%20report%20on%20the%20formation%20of%20the%20squads.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EReuters%20wasn't%20able%20to%20determine%20how%20many%20soldiers%20in%20total%20are%20serving%20in%20the%20units%2C%20though%20the%20interviews%20with%20the%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter%20point%20to%20at%20least%20several%20hundred%20Storm-Z%20fighters%20currently%20being%20deployed%20on%20the%20frontline.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWagner%20had%20about%2025%2C000%20fighters%20engaged%20in%20the%20conflict%2C%20its%20late%20leader%20Yevgeny%20Prigozhin%20said%20at%20the%20time%20of%20his%20June%20mutiny.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPresident%20Vladimir%20Putin%20made%20reference%20to%20convicts%20fighting%20in%20the%20regular%20army%20on%20Friday.%20At%20a%20televised%20meeting%20with%20a%20small%20group%20of%20regular%20Russian%20servicemen%2C%20he%20said%20he%20was%20aware%20that%20two%20of%20their%20comrades%2C%20former%20prison%20inmates%2C%20had%20been%20killed%20in%20action.%20%26quot%3BThey%20gave%20their%20lives%20for%20the%20motherland%20and%20have%20fully%20absolved%20themselves%20of%20their%20guilt%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Putin%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20convicts'%20families%20would%20be%20given%20help%2C%20without%20elaborating.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20historical%20precedent%20for%20military%20offenders%20being%20pressed%20into%20fighting%20units%3B%20in%201942%2C%20when%20the%20Red%20Army%20was%20retreating%20from%20a%20Nazi%20advance%2C%20Soviet%20leader%20Josef%20Stalin%20ordered%20soldiers%20who%20panicked%20or%20left%20their%20posts%20into%20%26quot%3Bpunishment%20battalions%26quot%3B%20deployed%20to%20the%20most%20dangerous%20parts%20of%20the%20front%2C%20according%20to%20a%20decree%20he%20signed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUkraine's%20government%20has%20said%20it%20also%20releases%20some%20convicts%20if%20they%20agree%20to%20fight%20in%20the%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFROM%20CUSTODY%20TO%20CARNAGE%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EStorm-Z%20is%20an%20unofficial%20term%20used%20by%20Russian%20troops%2C%20combining%20a%20term%20for%20assault%20troops%20with%20the%20letter%20Z%2C%20adopted%20by%20the%20military%20as%20a%20symbol%20of%20their%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EArtyom%20Shchikin%2C%20a%2029-year-old%20from%20the%20Mordovia%20region%20in%20central%20Russia%2C%20was%20serving%20a%20two-year%20sentence%20for%20robbery%20handed%20down%20in%20December%202021%20when%20defence%20ministry%20recruiters%20came%20to%20his%20jail%20asking%20if%20inmates%20wanted%20to%20go%20and%20fight%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20according%20to%20court%20records%20and%20two%20of%20his%20relatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20signed%20up%20because%2C%20even%20though%20he%20was%20scheduled%20for%20release%20in%20December%20this%20year%2C%20he%20wanted%20to%20wipe%20clean%20his%20criminal%20record%20plus%20earn%20money%20so%20his%20family%20could%20renovate%20their%20home%2C%20his%20family%20members%20said.%20Three%20Storm-Z%20fighters%20said%20they%20were%20offered%20wages%20of%20about%20200%2C000%20roubles%20(%242%2C000)%20per%20month%2C%20though%20said%20they%20had%20been%20paid%20roughly%20half%20that%20amount%2C%20on%20average.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBy%20May%20this%20year%2C%20Shchikin%20was%20assigned%20to%20a%20penal%20unit%20within%20the%20291st%20Guards%20Motorised%20Rifle%20Regiment%20and%20deployed%20to%20the%20Zaporizhzhia%20region%20in%20southern%20Ukraine%2C%20where%20Kyiv's%20forces%20are%20trying%20to%20break%20through%20Russian%20defences%2C%20the%20relatives%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAn%20official%20with%20the%20regimental%20headquarters%20didn't%20respond%20to%20Reuters%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVladimir%20Rogov%2C%20an%20official%20in%20the%20Russian-installed%20administration%20in%20Zaporizhzhia%20who%20gives%20regular%20online%20updates%20about%20the%20conflict%2C%20has%20posted%20on%20Telegram%20that%20the%20291st%20regiment%20was%20fighting%20in%20the%20region%20throughout%20the%20summer.%20Rogov%20didn't%20respond%20to%20a%20Reuters%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShchikin's%20relatives%20last%20heard%20from%20him%20on%20June%2018.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDays%20later%2C%20his%20unit's%20positions%20came%20under%20Ukrainian%20fire%2C%20the%20relatives%20said%2C%20citing%20conversations%20with%20two%20survivors%20from%20Shchikin's%20squad.%20Three%20comrades%20who%20had%20been%20in%20a%20trench%20with%20him%20were%20killed%2C%20another%20had%20his%20hand%20torn%20off%2C%20while%20Shchikin%20himself%20is%20missing%2C%20the%20relatives%20said.%20His%20body%20hasn't%20been%20recovered.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShchikin's%20relatives%20said%20when%20they%20asked%20the%20defence%20ministry%20for%20answers%20about%20his%20fate%2C%20it%20either%20didn't%20respond%20or%20didn't%20give%20any%20definitive%20answers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20were%20from%20a%20Storm%20unit.%20For%20them%2C%20no%20one%20is%20going%20to%20be%20in%20a%20rush%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20one%20relative.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EReuters%20was%20unable%20to%20independently%20confirm%20the%20relatives'%20account%20of%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDRUNK%20ON%20DUTY%2C%20USING%20DRUGS%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20convicts%20form%20the%20core%20of%20the%20penal%20squads%2C%20some%20regular%20soldiers%20have%20been%20assigned%20to%20them%20as%20punishment%20for%20breaking%20discipline%2C%20according%20to%20two%20soldiers%20who%20said%20members%20of%20their%20units%20had%20been%20transferred%20in%20this%20way%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20Storm-Z%20fighter%20called%20Igor%2C%20a%20convict%20jailed%20for%20attempted%20murder.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20soldiers%2C%20including%20the%20one%20from%20unit%20no.%2040318%2C%20said%20officers%20had%20sent%20soldiers%20to%20Storm-Z%20for%20being%20drunk%20on%20duty%2C%20for%20using%20drugs%2C%20and%20for%20refusing%20to%20carry%20out%20orders.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A0According%20to%20Russian%20legislation%20on%20military%20discipline%2C%20a%20soldier%20can%20only%20be%20transferred%20to%20a%20penal%20unit%20if%20convicted%20by%20a%20military%20court.%20None%20of%20the%20people%20who%20told%20Reuters%20of%20soldiers%20being%20sent%20to%20Storm-Z%20said%20the%20men%20had%20participated%20in%20a%20court%20hearing.%20Contacted%20last%20week%2C%20the%20soldier%20from%20unit%20no.%2040318%20said%20there%20were%20no%20court%20hearings%20involved%20in%20such%20transfers%2C%20and%20Igor%2C%20the%20Storm-Z%20fighter%2C%20said%20he%20had%20no%20knowledge%20of%20court%20hearings%20having%20taken%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Geneva%20convention%2C%20a%20set%20of%20international%20rules%20of%20war%2C%20doesn't%20cover%20soldiers%20being%20punished%20by%20their%20own%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREVOLT%20OF%20STORM-Z%20FIGHTERS%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20group%20of%20about%2020%20Storm-Z%20fighters%20in%20Zaporizhzhia%2C%20who%20were%20part%20of%20unit%20number%2022179%2C%20decided%20they'd%20had%20enough%20of%20their%20treatment%2C%20refused%20an%20order%20to%20go%20back%20to%20the%20frontline%2C%20and%20recorded%20a%20June%2028%20video%20complaining%20about%20their%20treatment.%20Reuters%20called%20numbers%20listed%20for%20the%20unit%2C%20but%20they%20were%20out%20of%20operation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20the%20frontline%2C%20where%20we've%20been%2C%20we%20did%20not%20get%20deliveries%20of%20ammunition.%20We%20did%20not%20get%20water%20or%20food.%20The%20injured%20were%20not%20taken%20away%3A%20still%20now%20the%20dead%20are%20rotting%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20fighter%20in%20the%20video%2C%20whom%20Reuters%20was%20unable%20to%20identify.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20given%20dreadful%20orders%20that%20are%20not%20even%20worth%20carrying%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BWe%20refuse%20to%20continue%20carrying%20out%20combat%20missions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EReuters%20established%20the%20identities%20of%20two%20of%20the%20fighters%20involved%20in%20the%20revolt%2C%20and%20spoke%20to%20a%20relative%20of%20each%20man%20who%20corroborated%20the%20account%20in%20the%20video%2C%20which%20was%20published%20on%20June%2028%20by%20Gulagu.net%2C%20a%20France-based%20campaign%20group%20for%20Russian%20prisoners'%20rights%2C%20and%20reviewed%20by%20Reuters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20video%20was%20published%2C%C2%A0military%20police%20officers%20beat%20up%20the%20two%20fighters%2C%20and%20others%20in%20their%20squad%2C%20as%20punishment%20for%20their%20revolt%2C%20the%20two%20relatives%20said.%20Since%20then%2C%20they%20said%20the%20two%20fighters%20had%20told%20them%20that%20conditions%20had%20improved%20but%20they%20did%20not%20know%20when%20the%20men%20would%20be%20allowed%20to%20quit%20the%20military.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERussian%20officials%20have%20made%20no%20public%20comment%20about%20the%20incident%2C%20and%20the%20defence%20ministry%20didn't%20reply%20to%20Reuters%20queries.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20member%20of%20one%20of%20the%20soldiers%20in%20the%20revolt%2C%20a%20man%20from%20Siberia%20who%20had%20volunteered%20to%20join%20Storm-Z%20from%20prison%2C%20said%20she%20dreaded%20news%20from%20the%20front.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20God%2C%20let%20this%20end%20soon%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20of%20the%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696318620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F7nbqs8j8_stormz-squad-russia-reuters_625x300_03_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Frussia-deploys-punishment-battalions-to-frontlines-theyre-just-meat-4444506%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Drunk%20recruits.%20Insubordinate%20soldiers.%20Convicts.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Frussia-deploys-punishment-battalions-to-frontlines-theyre-just-meat-4444506%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Frussia-deploys-punishment-battalions-to-frontlines-theyre-just-meat-4444506%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Frussia-deploys-punishment-battalions-to-frontlines-theyre-just-meat-4444506%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Aamir%20announces%20'Lahore%2C%201947'%20with%20Sunny%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696318560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104126797%2Cimgsize-44378.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Faamir-khan-to-produce-sunny-deol-rajkumar-santoshis-lahore-1947%2Farticleshow%2F104126791.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F104126791.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EEnding%20all%20speculations%2C%20Aamir%20Khan%20has%20finally%20announced%20his%20next%20collaboration%20with%20Sunny%20Deol.%20The%20actor%20confirmed%20the%20name%20of%20the%20movie%20and%20revealed%20that%20it%20will%20be%20helmed%20by%20Rajkumar%20Santoshi.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Faamir-khan-to-produce-sunny-deol-rajkumar-santoshis-lahore-1947%2Farticleshow%2F104126791.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22NIA%20Conducts%20Co-Ordinated%20Raids%20on%20Rights%20Activists%20Across%2062%20Locations%20in%20Andhra%2C%20Telangana%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F06145703%2FUntitled-design-3.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EMumbai%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Officials%20of%20the%20National%20Investigating%20Agency%20(NIA)%20arrived%20in%20groups%20of%20four%20and%20five%20in%2062%20locations%20across%20Telangana%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20on%20October%202%2C%20in%20coordinated%20raids%20at%20the%20homes%20of%20human%20rights%20activists%20and%20researchers.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20raid%20teams%20%E2%80%93%20comprising%20of%20NIA%20officers%20from%20Delhi%20and%20the%20local%20police%20%E2%80%93%20arrived%20between%205.30%20am%20and%206%20am%20on%20the%20day%2C%20and%20stayed%20at%20the%20locations%20till%20afternoon.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20such%20raid%20was%20carried%20out%20at%20the%20house%20of%20a%20senior%20lawyer%20and%20rights%20activist%20Durba%20Suresh%20Kumar.%20Suresh%2C%20also%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Indian%20Association%20of%20People%E2%80%99s%20Lawyer%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20he%20was%20woken%20up%20by%20the%20NIA%20sleuths.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20woken%20up%20by%20the%20officers.%20They%20had%20flown%20down%2C%20along%20with%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Epanch%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20witnesses.%20But%20the%20local%20police%20were%20not%20informed%2C%E2%80%9D%20Suresh%20said.%20The%20local%20police%2C%20Suresh%20says%2C%20joined%20much%20later.%20From%20Suresh%E2%80%99s%20house%2C%20the%20NIA%20seized%20his%20phone%20and%20a%2012-page%20pamphlet%20of%20the%20People%E2%80%99s%20War%20Group%2C%20dating%20back%20to%201993.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESuresh%20says%20for%20the%20longest%20period%2C%20he%20was%20not%20aware%20of%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20raid%20and%20the%20exact%20case%20in%20connection%20with%20which%20it%20was%20being%20conducted.%20The%20NIA%20later%20informed%20him%20that%20the%20ongoing%20raids%20were%20a%20part%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9CMunchingiputtu%20CPI%20(Maoist)%20conspiracy%20case%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20in%20connection%20with%20which%20similar%20raids%20were%20carried%20out%20at%20the%20residences%20of%20many%20rights%20activists%20and%20academics%20in%202021.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESuresh%20was%20served%20a%20notice%20under%20section%20160%20of%20the%20CrPC%2C%20asking%20him%20to%20be%20present%20before%20the%20NIA%20as%20a%20witness.%20This%2C%20Suresh%20points%20out%2C%20is%20both%20%E2%80%9Cunlawful%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cunethical%E2%80%9D.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20a%20counsel%20for%20many%20persons%20named%20in%20the%20case.%20I%20represent%20them%20in%20the%20high%20court%20and%20now%20the%20NIA%20wants%20me%20to%20appear%20before%20them%20as%20a%20witness%20in%20the%20same%20case%2C%E2%80%9D%20Suresh%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20over%20a%20phone%20call.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20a%20lawyer%20has%20been%20named%20an%20accused%20or%20asked%20to%20be%20a%20witness%20in%20the%20same%20case%20they%20have%20appeared%20as%20counsel%20in%2C%20before%20a%20court.%20Surendra%20Gadling%2C%20a%20Nagpur-based%20lawyer%20and%20an%20accused%20in%20the%20Elgar%20Parishad%20case%2C%20was%20also%20made%20an%20accused%20in%20one%20of%20the%20cases%20in%20which%20he%20had%20defended%20an%20accused%20in%20the%20conflict-affected%20Vidarbha%20region%20in%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHRF%20functionaries%20targeted%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOf%20the%2062%20locations%20raided%2C%2053%20are%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20nine%20are%20in%20Telangana.%20Along%20with%20the%20raids%20on%20October%202%2C%20the%20NIA%20also%20arrested%20one%20Chandra%20Narasimhulu%2C%20allegedly%20a%20state%20executive%20committee%20member%20of%20the%20Pragathiseela%20Karmika%20Samakya%20(PKS)%2C%20an%20alleged%20front%20organisation%20of%20the%20banned%20CPI%20(Maoist).%20Narasimhulu%20was%20arrested%20from%20Satya%20Sai%20district%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20Along%20with%20his%20arrest%2C%20the%20NIA%20has%20claimed%20to%20have%20found%20a%20pistol%2C%2014%20rounds%20of%20ammunition%2C%20and%20Rs%2013%20lakhs%20in%20a%20case%20from%20another%20spot%20in%20Kadapa%20district.%20Maoist%20literature%20and%20pamphlets%20were%20also%20seized%2C%20the%20NIA%20has%20claimed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMost%20of%20those%20raided%20were%20unsure%20if%20they%20are%20being%20looked%20at%20as%20suspects%20or%20witnesses%20in%20the%20case.%20The%20house%20of%20K.%20Sudha%2C%20a%20state%20executive%20committee%20member%20of%20Human%20Rights%20Forum%2C%20was%20also%20raided.%20Sudha%2C%20who%20reaches%20at%20a%20state%20law%20university%2C%20said%20the%20NIA%20has%20taken%20her%20phone%20away.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20raids%20took%20place%20at%20Sudha%E2%80%99s%20house%2C%20V.S.%20Krishna%2C%20the%20convener%20of%20the%20HRF%E2%80%99s%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20Telangana%20units%20reached%20Sudha%E2%80%99s%20residence.%20Krishna%E2%80%99s%20house%20was%20raided%20in%202021%20in%20the%20same%20case.%20Krishna%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20he%20got%20calls%20from%20two%20other%20HRF%20members%2C%20who%20said%20that%20the%20NIA%20broke%20into%20their%20houses%20because%20they%20were%20not%20home%20when%20officials%20arrived.%20%E2%80%9CI%20tried%20contacting%20other%20members.%20When%20Sudha%20did%20not%20pick%20up%20the%20call%2C%20I%20knew%20the%20NIA%20had%20reached%20her%20place%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20Krishna%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20two%20other%20person%E2%80%99s%20whose%20houses%20were%20raided%20when%20they%20were%20away%20are%20HRF%E2%80%99s%20AP%20state%20general%20secretary%20Y.%20Rajesh%20in%20Amalapuram%20and%20the%20organisation%E2%80%99s%20state%20vice-president%20K.V.%20Jagannadha%20Rao%20in%20Srikakulam.%20Rajesh%2C%20who%20was%20on%20his%20way%20back%20from%20Bengaluru%2C%20when%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20called%20him%20late%20on%20October%202%2C%20said%20that%20the%20NIA%20contacted%20him%20a%20little%20before%206%20am.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20came%20with%20a%20notice%20under%20Section%20165%20(2)%20of%20the%20CrPc%2C%20which%20authorised%20them%20to%20search%20the%20premise.%20Some%20of%20my%20neighbours%20went%20to%20my%20place%20and%20the%20NIA%20conducted%20the%20raid%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rajesh%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20NIA%20has%20not%20made%20any%20seizures%20from%20his%20house.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBooks%2C%20vernacular%20literature%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20from%20another%20HRF%20functionary%E2%80%99s%20place%2C%20the%20NIA%20has%20picked%20up%20over%2060%20books.%20Sudha%2C%20who%20shared%20information%20about%20the%20raid%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20basically%20picked%20up%20every%20book%20and%20document%20that%20had%20red%20font%20on%20it.%E2%80%9D%20Krishna%20said%20the%20officers%20did%20not%20know%20to%20read%20Telugu.%20%E2%80%9CMost%20books%20and%20our%20write-ups%20are%20in%20the%20local%20language.%20They%20mindlessly%20picked%20things%20up%20and%20later%20call%20it%20incriminating%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBesides%20HRF%20and%20IAPL%2C%20houses%20of%20the%20members%20of%20the%20Civil%20Liberties%20Committee%20(CLC)%2C%20the%20Committee%20for%20the%20Release%20of%20Political%20Prisoners%20(CRPP)%2C%20and%20the%20Revolutionary%20Writers%20Association%20(RWA)%2C%20were%20also%20raided%20among%20others.%20The%20NIA%20has%20accused%20veteran%20rights%20activists%20and%20organisations%20of%20acting%20as%20%E2%80%9Cfronts%E2%80%9D%20to%20the%20CPI%20(Maoist)%20organisation%2C%20banned%20in%202009.%20This%20claim%20has%20been%20vehemently%20opposed%20by%20rights%20organisations.%20HRF%20has%20called%20the%20NIA%E2%80%99s%20claim%20%E2%80%9Ca%20plain%20canard%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CSeeking%20to%20criminalise%20our%20human%20rights%20activity%20will%20never%20succeed.%20HRF%20is%20not%20an%20appendage%20of%20the%20Maoists%20or%20any%20other%20political%20party.%20HRF%20was%20formed%20on%20October%2011%2C%201998%20and%20we%20have%20turned%2025%20this%20month.%20We%20shall%20persist%20in%20spreading%20a%20human%20rights%20culture%20in%20society%20with%20the%20certitude%20that%20a%20broad-based%20and%20truly%20independent%20human%20rights%20movement%20is%20desirable%20and%20possible%2C%E2%80%9D%20HRF%20said%2C%20in%20a%20press%20statement%20released%20earlier%20today%2C%20October%203.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20locations%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20subjected%20to%20raids%20are%20in%20Guntur%2C%20Palanadu%2C%20Vijayawada%2C%20Rajhmundry%2C%20Prakasam%2C%20Bapatla%2C%20Eluru%2C%20East%20Godawari%2C%20Dr%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%20Konasema%2C%20Visakhapatnam%2C%20Vizianagaram%2C%20Nellore%2C%20Tirupati%2C%20Kadapa%2C%20Anantpur%2C%20and%20Kurnool%20districts.%20The%20NIA%20said%20that%20the%20nine%20locations%20in%20Telangana%20include%20districts%20of%20Hyderabad%2C%20Mahabubnagar%2C%20Hanumakonda%2C%20Ranga%20Reddy%2C%20and%20Adilabad.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20investigation%2C%20first%20registered%20and%20handled%20by%20the%20local%20state%20police%20in%202020%2C%20was%20taken%20up%20by%20the%20NIA%20in%202021.%20Popularly%20known%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98Munchingiputtu%20case%E2%80%99%2C%20it%20deals%20with%20alleged%20Maoist%20movement%20and%20literature%20in%20a%20village%20of%20the%20Alluri%20Sitharama%20Raju%3Cbr%3E%20district.%20The%20NIA%20has%20filed%20a%20chargesheet%20against%20seven%20persons%20in%20that%20case.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20the%20immediate%20causes%20for%20worry%20expressed%20by%20those%20raided%20is%20around%20the%20seizure%20of%20electronic%20devices.%20Most%20of%20them%20are%20lawyers%20and%20researchers%20and%20very%20heavily%20reliant%20on%20their%20electronic%20devices%20for%20their%20work.%20%E2%80%9CSeizure%20of%20electronic%20devices%20including%20mobiles%20without%20even%20providing%20cloned%20copies%20to%20the%20owners%20amounts%20to%20immediate%20lack%20of%20access%20to%20precious%20work-related%20material%20and%20contacts.%20It%20leads%20to%20an%20overwhelming%20loss%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20HRF%20statement%20reads.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20confiscate%20these%20devices%20in%20such%20a%20sudden%20manner%20results%20in%20a%20stunning%20dispossession.%20It%20is%20not%20only%20a%20deprival%20of%20valuable%20property%20of%20the%20functionaries%20concerned%20but%20also%20of%20their%20right%20to%20livelihood%2C%20privacy%20and%20human%20dignity.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696318456000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F06145703%2FUntitled-design-3.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fnia-raids-62-andhra-pradesh-telangana-maoist%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20raids%20were%20in%20connection%20with%20the%202021%20Munchingiputtu%20CPI%20(Maoist)%20conspiracy%20case.%20Devices%20and%20literature%20belonging%20to%20functionaries%20and%20lawyers%20of%20the%20Indian%20Association%20of%20People's%20Lawyer%20and%20Human%20Rights%20Forum%2C%20along%20with%20various%20other%20rights%20bodies%20were%20seized.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fnia-raids-62-andhra-pradesh-telangana-maoist%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22No%20Kohli!%20Just%20One%20Indian%20Star%20Included%20As%20Buttler%20Picks%20Dream%20ODI%20Team%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EEngland%20cricket%20team%20star%20Jos%20Buttler%20picked%20his%20dream%20five-a-side%20ODI%20team%20and%20just%20one%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20batter%20was%20able%20to%20make%20the%20cut.%20Buttler%20did%20not%20include%20Virat%20Kohli%20but%20instead%20went%20with%20the%20India%20skipper%20Virat%20Kohli.%20When%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20batters%2C%20Buttler%20included%20South%20Africa's%20Quinton%20De%20Kock%20along%20with%20Rohit%20and%20picked%20Australia's%20Glenn%20Maxwell%20as%20the%20all-rounder%20option.%20In%20the%20bowling%20department%2C%20he%20went%20for%20South%20Africa%20pacer%20Andrich%20Nortje%20and%20his%20England%20teammate%20Adil%20Rashid.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdil%20Rashid%20(England)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E184%20ODI%20wickets%20at%20an%20average%20of%2032.41%2C%20economy%205.67%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E11%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20wickets%20at%20an%20average%2047.81%2C%20economy%20of%205.71%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAdil's%20was%20Buttler's%20first%20selection-%20tipped%20to%20enjoy%20a%20successful%20trip%20to%20India%20next%20month%20as%20England%20attempt%20to%20defend%20their%20title.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBack%20in%202019%2C%20the%20leg-spinner%20got%2011%20scalps%20in%20his%20debut%20World%20Cup%20on%20home%20soil%2C%20including%20figures%20of%203%2F54%20(10)%20against%20Australia%2C%203%2F66%20(10)%20when%20taking%20on%20Afghanistan.%20His%20economy%20was%20under%20five%20an%20over%20against%20New%20Zealand%20in%20the%20final%2C%20where%20the%20side%20eventually%20lifted%20the%20trophy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERashid%20will%20be%20aiming%20to%20enjoy%20India's%20spin-friendly%20conditions%20and%20comes%20into%20the%20tournament%20boasting%20strong%20form%2C%20going%2010%20ODI%20matches%20on%20the%20trot%20taking%20at%20least%20one%20wicket.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%2010%20ODIs%2C%20Rashid%20has%20taken%2022%20wickets%20at%20an%20average%20of%2022.72%2C%20at%20an%20economy%20of%205.95%2C%20taking%20a%20wicket%20every%2023%20deliveries.%20He%20could%20pass%20the%20200%20wickets%20milestone%20during%20the%20tournament%2C%20with%2016%20more%20scalps%20to%20go.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQuinton%20de%20Kock%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E6%2C178%20ODI%20runs%20at%2044.75%2C%20Strike%20Rate%2095.75%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E450%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20runs%20at%2030.00%2C%20Strike%20Rate%2085.55%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E190%20catches%2C%2016%20stumpings%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E18%20catches%2C%201%20stumping%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%2030-year-old%20is%20pulling%20down%20the%20curtains%20on%20his%20ODI%20career%20after%20the%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%2C%20but%20his%20threat%20as%20a%20match-winner%20is%20still%20widely%20recognized%20ahead%20of%20Proteas%20campaign%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20strikes%20close%20to%20a%20run-a-ball%20in%20the%2050-over%20format%2C%20de%20Kock's%20average%20of%2044.75%20is%20great%2C%20considering%20the%20new%20ball%20challenges%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20order%20and%20his%20aggressive%2C%20high-risk%20approach%20with%20the%20bat.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20World%20Cups%2C%20de%20Kock%20has%20not%20made%20a%20huge%20score.%20He%20made%20three%20half-centuries%20at%20the%202019%20tournament%2C%20including%20a%20knock%20of%2068%20(74)%20against%20England%20and%2052%20(51)%20against%20Australia%20in%20a%20winning%20effort.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E10%2C031%20ODI%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%2048.69%2C%20Strike%20Rate%2090.26%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E978%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%2065.20%2C%20Strike%20Rate%2095.97%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHaving%20recently%2010%2C000%20ODI%20runs%2C%20the%20Indian%20skipper's%202019%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20campaign%20is%20fresh%20in%20everyone's%20memory.%20Bouncing%20back%20from%20the%20heartbreak%20of%20missing%20India's%202011%20squad%2C%20Rohit%20showed%20glimpses%20of%20his%20class%20with%20137%20(126)%20against%20Bangladesh%20and%20also%20two%20half-centuries%20at%20the%202015%20tournament.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%202019%20campaign%20for%20Rohit%20exceeded%20everyone's%20expectations%2C%20blasting%20five%20centuries%2C%20including%20three%20tons%20in%20successive%20knocks%20against%20England%2C%20Bangladesh%20and%20Sri%20Lanka.%20He%20scored%20648%20runs%20in%20the%20tournament%20with%20five%20tons%20and%20a%20fifty%2C%20ending%20up%20as%20leading%20run-scorer%20in%20the%20tournament.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERohit%20will%20most%20likely%20pass%201%2C000%20runs%20in%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20matches%2C%20with%20his%20average%20of%2065.20%20only%20bettered%20by%20one%20player%20to%20cross%20four%20four%20figures%20-%20South%20Africa's%20AB%20de%20Villiers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGlenn%20Maxwell%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E3%2C490%20ODI%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%2033.88%2C%20Strike%20Rate%20124.82%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E501%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%2038.53%2C%20Strike%20Rate%20169.25%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E60%20ODI%20wickets%20at%20an%20average%20of%2050.23%2C%20economy%205.56%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E6%20wickets%20at%20an%20average%20of%2085.50%2C%20Economy%205.89%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHighly%20regarded%20as%20a%20match-winner%20both%20with%20ball%20and%20bat%2C%20Maxwell%20was%20acknowledged%20by%20his%20English%20rival%2C%20and%20will%20be%20key%20for%20Australia%20in%20Indian%20conditions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202019%2C%20Maxwell%20was%20not%20blessed%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20opportunities%20with%20the%20bat%2C%20mostly%20taking%20to%20the%20crease%20in%20death-over%20situations%2C%20but%20in%202015%20campaign%2C%20Maxwell%20stepped%20up.%20He%20made%20a%20swashbuckling%20102%20(53)%20against%20Sri%20Lanka%20in%20Sydney%2C%20as%20well%20as%20quick-fire%20half-centuries%20against%20Afghanistan%20and%20England%20on%20the%20road%20to%20lifting%20the%20trophy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChurning%20runs%20out%20through%20the%20middle%20and%20death%20overs%20with%20the%20bat%2C%20Maxwell%20will%20also%20be%20useful%20with%20his%20off-spin%20and%20could%20be%20taking%20a%20greater%20responsibility%20on%20slower%20pitches.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnrich%20Nortje%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E36%20ODI%20wickets%20at%20an%20average%20of%2027.27%2C%20economy%205.85%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYet%20to%20play%20at%20a%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBattling%20Anrich%20Nortje%20is%20a%20headache%2C%20and%20Buttler%20knows%20first%20hand%2C%20dismissed%20by%20the%20Proteas%20quick%20in%20their%20first%20meeting%20in%20the%20ODI%20format%20back%20in%20January.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENortje's%20plan%20of%20hitting%20back%20of%20the%20length%20brought%20Buttler%20undone%20in%20Bloemfontein%2C%20who%20edged%20to%20Quinton%20de%20Kock.%20Buttler%20has%20scored%20only%2019%20runs%20off%2015%20balls%20against%20Nortje%20in%20the%20format%20aside%20from%20the%20dismissal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERuled%20out%20with%20a%20hand%20injury%20for%20the%202019%20tournament%2C%20the%202023%20competition%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20his%20first%20WC%2C%20but%20he%20was%20ruled%20out%20of%20the%20squad%20due%20to%20an%20injury%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696318320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F2pm63qug_jos-buttler-afp_625x300_08_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fno-