Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20injuries%20were%20certified%20by%20a%20Russian%20military%20hospital%20on%20March%2014%2C%20and%20the%20cause%20of%20his%20wounds%20was%20listed%20as%20improper%20handling%20of%20ammunition%20by%20someone%20in%20his%20unit%2C%20the%20ruling%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20corporal%20applied%20for%20a%20claim%20of%203%20million%20rubles%2C%20or%20%2430%2C000%2C%20according%20to%20the%20decision.%20Russia%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-troops-in-ukraine-shooting-themselves-avoid-war-memoir-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edisbursed%20these%20payments%20since%20early%202022%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20soldiers%20wounded%20in%20the%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20on%20May%2025%2C%20an%20investigation%20run%20by%20Kurazov's%20combat%20unit%20found%20that%20the%20corporal's%20wounds%20weren't%20directly%20associated%20with%20any%20combat%20missions%20or%20tasks%2C%20and%20instead%20were%20inflicted%20by%20the%20mistakes%20of%20another%20serviceman.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20ruled%20that%20there%20were%20no%20grounds%20for%20the%20corporal%20to%20receive%20the%20lump-sum%20payment%2C%20and%20Kurazov's%20commander%20ordered%20a%20refusal%20of%20the%20claim%2C%20the%20judicial%20decision%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20military%20court%20in%20the%20Nalchik%20Garrison%20also%20refused%20to%20grant%20Kurazov's%20payment%20on%20June%2027%2C%20per%20the%20court%20filing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKurazov%20argued%20that%20the%20one-time%20payment%20to%20injured%20troops%20should%20be%20given%20to%20any%20Russian%20soldier%20wounded%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20including%20the%20Donetsk%20and%20Luhansk%20regions%2C%20the%20filing%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20appealed%20the%20Nalchik%20Garrison%20military%20court's%20decision%2C%20bringing%20his%20case%20to%20the%20southern%20district%20military%20court%20in%20Rostov-on-Don%20in%20August.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20panel%20of%20three%20military%20court%20judges%20%E2%80%94%20Viktor%20Alekseevich%20Kostin%2C%20Dmitry%20Viktorovich%20Merkulov%2C%20and%20Magomedbasir%20Gapurovich%20Shuaipov%20%E2%80%94%20ruled%20on%20September%208%20that%20the%20original%20decision%20should%20be%20upheld.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20agreed%20that%20requirements%20for%20the%20%2430%2C000%20payment%20include%20the%20soldier%20being%20wounded%20in%20direct%20combat.%20However%2C%20they%20added%20that%20Kurazov%20has%20the%20right%20to%20apply%20for%20other%20types%20of%20compensation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKurazov's%20refused%20claim%20is%20one%20of%20several%20that%20have%20been%20contested%20by%20injured%20Russian%20soldiers%2C%20such%20as%20contract%20soldier%20Aziz%20Magomedov%2C%20who%20was%20denied%20payment%20after%20receiving%20initial%20treatment%20in%20April%202022%20at%20a%20city%20hospital%20instead%20of%20a%20military%20one%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kavkazr.com%2Fa%2Fkontraktniku-iz-dagestana-otkazali-v-vyplate-za-poluchennuyu-v-ukraine-travmu%2F32113512.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERadio%20Free%20Liberty%20reported.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussia's%20Defense%20Ministry%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20Insider's%20request%20for%20comment%20sent%20outside%20regular%20business%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-soldier-denied-compensation-3-million-rubles-friendly-fire-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696313028000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F651ba6d142ecf94db476132e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-soldier-denied-compensation-3-million-rubles-friendly-fire-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Corporal%20Khizri%20Kurazov%20was%20wounded%20by%20a%20mine%20that%20was%20accidentally%20detonated%20by%20a%20fellow%20Russian%20soldier%2C%20according%20to%20a%20court%20ruling%20against%20him.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ml