patients-including-12-newborns-die-in-maharashtra-hospital-in-a-day-official-cites-shortage-of-medicines-4443370%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ENDTV%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Ehas%20quoted%20in-charge%20dean%20of%20the%20hospital%2C%20S.R.%20Wakode%2C%20as%20saying%20that%20the%2024%20patients%20succumbed%20to%20death%20owing%20to%20various%20ailments%20though%20mostly%20snake%20bites.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20an%20institute%20Haffkine.%20We%20are%20supposed%20to%20buy%20medicines%20from%20them%2C%20but%20that%20also%20didn%E2%80%99t%20happen.%20But%20we%20did%20buy%20medicines%20locally%20and%20provided%20them%20to%20the%20patients%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20in-charge%20dean%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fpune%2Fmaharashtra-24-deaths-in-24-hours-at-nanded-civil-hospital-govt-orders-probe%2Farticleshow%2F104111166.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20quoted%20Wakode%C2%A0%20as%20saying%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20sanctioned%20budget%20for%20medicines%20too%20falls%20short%20due%20to%20heavy%20flow%20of%20patients%20%5Bincluding%5D%20from%20that%20of%20neighbouring%20districts%20of%20Telangana.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20always%20ensure%20that%20a%20patient%20does%20not%20lose%20his%20life%20due%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20essential%20medicines%20at%20our%20hospital.%20In%20such%20situations%2C%20we%20purchase%20medicines%20from%20the%20local%20budget.%20We%20cannot%20deny%20that%20sometimes%20there%20may%20be%20shortage%20of%20medicines%20for%20non-essential%20ailments%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20the%20hospital%20sought%20to%20distance%20itself%20from%20the%20dean%E2%80%99s%20statement.%20%E2%80%9CEssential%20medicines%20are%20available%20in%20the%20hospital.%20The%20hospital%20has%20Rs%2012%20crore%20in%20funds.%20For%20this%20financial%20year%2C%20Rs%204%20crore%20has%20been%20approved.%20Other%20patients%20are%20being%20treated%20as%20necessary%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said%20in%20a%20press%20release.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20dean%20also%20said%20that%20due%20to%20some%20staff%20members%20being%20posted%20out%20of%20the%20hospital.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20faced%20some%20difficulty%20since%20various%20staff%20were%20being%20transferred%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOut%20of%20the%2012%20adults%20who%20died%2C%20four%20have%20died%20due%20to%20heart%20attack%2C%20and%20others%20have%20died%20due%20to%20accidental%20injuries%2C%20complications%20during%20delivery%20and%20kidney%20failure%20among%20other%20complications.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20opposition%20leaders%20have%20launched%20an%20attack%20on%20the%20government%20demanding%20answers%20on%20these%20deaths.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20lack%20of%20medical%20facilities%20and%20staff.%20Many%20nurses%20were%20transferred%20and%20their%20replacements%20were%20not%20given.%20Many%20machines%20are%20not%20working.%20The%20hospital%E2%80%99s%20capacity%20is%20500%2C%20but%201%2C200%20patients%20are%20admitted%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.freepressjournal.in%2Fmumbai%2Fmaharashtra-12-infants-among-24-dead-in-nanded-govt-hospital-in-past-24-hours-dean-cites-medicine-staff-shortage%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EFree%20Press%20Journal%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20quoted%20former%20state%20chief%20minister%20Ashok%20Chavan%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20will%20speak%20to%20Ajit%20Pawar%20(about%20this).%20The%20government%20should%20look%20into%20the%20matter%20keenly%20and%20take%20control%20of%20the%20situation%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Congress%20leader%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E