as%20and%20themes%20dominating%20the%20conversation%20in%20India%20and%20the%20world.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20shift%20towards%20digitalisation%20in%20India%20has%20been%20led%20by%20the%20private%20sector%2C%20and%20Aadhaar%20is%20often%20cited%20as%20a%20driver%20of%20social%20and%20economic%20development.%20While%20civil%20society%20has%20largely%20focused%20on%20civil%20liberties%20concerns%20such%20as%20privacy%2C%20it%20is%20also%20important%20to%20consider%20the%20accountability%20implications%20of%20digitalisation.%20Systems%20are%20being%20made%20more%20opaque%20than%20ever%20and%20governments%20are%20insulated%20by%20regulators%20who%20hide%20behind%20technology%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20being%20transparent.%20This%20ends%20up%20denying%20the%20benefits%20of%20digitisation%20to%20the%20people%2C%20and%20instead%20bringing%20them%20great%20risks%20and%20hardships.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERegulatory%20silences%20can%20be%20costly%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20shocking%20incident%2C%20TamilNad%20Mercantile%20Bank%20mistakenly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Fcities%2Fchennai%2Fstory%2Fchennai-cab-driver-receives-rs-9000-crore-deposit-in-bank-account-2438492-2023-09-21%5C%22%3Edeposited%20Rs%209%2C000%20crore%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20account%20of%20a%20cab%20driver%20in%20Chennai.%20The%20driver%20was%20able%20to%20transact%20up%20to%20Rs%2021%2C000%20before%20the%20erroneous%20transaction%20was%20reversed.%20He%20was%20later%20contacted%20by%20the%20nearest%20branch%20officials%20who%20instructed%20him%20to%20remain%20tight-lipped%20about%20the%20incident%2C%20but%20subsequently%20he%20was%20threatened%20to%20repay%20the%20money%20spent%20or%20face%20consequences.%20An%20unknown%20cash%20deposit%20into%20his%20account%20for%20Rs%2011%2C000%20and%20offers%20for%20a%20car%20loan%20to%20remain%20silent%20about%20the%20episode%20later%20forced%20him%20to%20go%20public%20about%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20CEO%20of%20the%20bank%20has%20now%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fbusiness%2F2023%2Fsep%2F29%2Ftmb-md-ceo-s-krishnan-quits-citing-personal-reasons-2619222.html%5C%22%3Eresigned%20citing%20%E2%80%98personal%20reasons%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20mistake%20was%20caused%20by%20a%20combination%20of%20factors%2C%20including%20invalid%20account%20numbers%20and%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fstates%2Ftamil-nadu%2F2023%2Fsep%2F23%2Fno-financial-loss-to-bank-says-tmb-in-communication-to-nse-bse-over-wrongly-credited-rs-9k-crore-2617395.html%5C%22%3Esoftware%20bug%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20National%20Automated%20Clearing%20House%20(NACH)%20application%2C%20a%20system%20widely%20used%20for%20salary%20payments%2FEMIs.%20While%20the%20bank%20was%20able%20to%20reverse%20the%20transaction%20quickly%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20note%20that%20such%20incidents%20could%20have%20serious%20consequences%20for%20customers%20and%20financial%20institutions%20alike%2C%20especially%20in%20this%20era%20when%20individuals%20have%20instant%20payments%20at%20their%20fingertips%20and%20can%20move%20money%20faster%20than%20ever%20before.%20It%20must%20be%20remembered%20that%20a%20similar%20software%20bug%20in%20SWIFT%20(financial%20messaging%20system)%20was%20cited%20as%20the%20reason%20behind%20the%20Nirav%20Modi%20fraud%20involving%20the%20Punjab%20National%20Bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20highlights%20serious%20gaps%20in%20critical%20legacy%20payment%20systems%20like%20the%20NACH%20system%2C%20run%20by%20the%20National%20Payments%20Corporation%20of%20India%20(NPCI)%2C%20and%20the%20need%20for%20active%20regulation.%20The%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%2C%20while%20being%20detailedly%20prescriptive%20citing%20consumer%20protection%20(to%20the%20extent%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finc42.com%2Ffeatures%2Frecurring-payment-conundrum-how-guidelines-have-shaken-indias-subscription-economy%2F%5C%22%3Ebringing%20them%20hardship%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20with%20the%20recurring%20payments%20fiasco)%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20card%20networks%20and%20prepaid%20instruments%2C%20actively%20chooses%20to%20remain%20blind%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20supervising%20and%20under-regulates%20the%20payments%20systems%20run%20by%20NPCI%2C%20leading%20to%20issues%20such%20as%20these.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20RBI%20should%20actively%20publish%20detailed%20reports%20on%20the%20quality%20of%20its%20supervision%20of%20regulated%20entities%20and%20conduct%20periodic%20reviews%20of%20all%20payment%20systems%20with%20all%20stakeholders%2C%20including%20members%20of%20the%20public%2C%20to%20maintain%20public%20trust%20in%20the%20regulatory%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMoody%E2%80%99s%20commentary%20on%20Aadhaar%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMoody%E2%80%99s%20Investors%20Service%2C%20a%20global%20rating%20agency%2C%20has%20raised%20concerns%20about%20security%20and%20privacy%20vulnerabilities%20in%20centralised%20identification%20systems%20like%20India%E2%80%99s%20Aadhaar%20programme.%20Moody%E2%80%99s%20in%20its%20report%20had%20said%20that%20Aadhaar%E2%80%99s%20system%20often%20results%20in%20service%20denials%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Famid-indias-global-digital-public-infrastructure-pitch-moodys-questions-aadhaar-efficacy%2Farticle67342025.ece%5C%22%3Equestioned%20the%20reliability%20of%20biometric%20technologies%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20especially%20for%20manual%20labourers%20in%20hot%2C%20humid%20climates.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20Ministry%20of%20Electronics%20%26amp%3B%20IT%20while%20dismissing%20the%20concerns%20and%20said%20Moody%E2%80%99s%20report%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleaseIframePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1960718%5C%22%3Edoes%20not%20cite%20either%20primary%20or%20secondary%20data%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20research%20in%20support%20of%20the%20opinions%20presented%20in%20it%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20UIDAI%20only%20publishes%20cumulative%20transaction%20data%20by%20provider%20on%20its%20dashboard%20and%20has%20not%20released%20any%20data%20on%20failures.%20This%20is%20also%20similar%20to%20how%20statistics%20on%20UPI%2FAadhaar-based%20direct%20benefit%20transfers%20are%20published%2C%20but%20there%20is%20no%20official%20number%20of%20UPI%20fraudulent%20transactions%2FAadhaar-Enabled%20Payment%20System%20biometric%20frauds.%20If%20the%20government%2Fregulators%20don%E2%80%99t%20publish%20official%20data%20that%20is%20uncomfortable%2C%20it%20is%20impossible%20to%20cite.%20Moody%E2%80%99s%20does%20cite%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Ffaulty-biometrics-duplication-errors-what-cag-audit-report-says-about-aadhaar-regime%5C%22%3ECAG%20report%20on%20UIDAI%3C%2Fa%3E%20while%20indicating%20biometric%20reliability.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndians%20have%20been%20the%20guinea%20pigs%20to%20pilot%20the%20Centralised%20Digital%20ID%20system%20and%20the%20success%20of%20Aadhaar%20equally%20lies%20in%20under-reporting%20failures%20and%20narrative%20management.%20The%20Moody%E2%80%99s%20report%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20when%20India%20is%20attempting%20to%20sell%20this%20technical%20prowess%20through%20the%20G20%20and%20a%20credible%20reply%20to%20the%20allegations%20would%20be%20to%20publish%20hard%20data%20%E2%80%93%20on%20biometric%20reliability%20and%20data%20points%20on%20new%20facial%20authentication%20modality%2C%20which%20is%20touted%20as%20response%20to%20both%20failures%20and%20fraud%20prevention%20that%20is%20prevalent%20in%20fingerprint-based%20biometric%20verification.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECentral%20Bank%20Digital%20Currency%20about%20which%20the%20RBI%20has%20no%20data%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%2C%20in%20response%20to%20an%20RTI%2C%20has%20said%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.medianama.com%2F2023%2F09%2F223-rbi-no-statistics-digital-rupee-rti%2F%5C%22%3Ehas%20no%20data%20on%20the%20Central%20Bank%20Digital%20Currency%20(CBDC)%2C%20eRupee-Retail%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20issues.%20CBDCs%20are%20piloted%20by%20several%20central%20banks%20as%20a%20regulated%20alternative%20to%20cryptocurrencies.%20The%20RBI%20came%20down%20strongly%20on%20cryptocurrencies%20originally%20through%20a%20shadow%20ban%20and%20was%20restrained%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20and%20the%20government%20later%20introduced%20crypto%20taxation%20to%20restrict%20the%20free%20outflow%20of%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20monetary%20sovereignty%20arguments%20might%20have%20legitimate%20state%20interest%2C%20and%20would%20be%20well%20within%20the%20purview%20of%20the%20central%20bank%20to%20have%20a%20strong%20opinion%20on%2C%20the%20same%20has%20to%20be%20matched%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20transparency%20too.%20Demonetisation%20(including%20the%20ongoing%20removal%20of%20the%20Rs%202%2C000%20note%20from%20supply%2C%20which%20got%20an%20additional%20one%20week%20extension)%20made%20the%20central%20bank%20far%20more%20transparent%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20money%20supply.%20We%20cannot%20go%20back%20to%20a%20world%20where%20the%20central%20bank%20says%20it%20has%20no%20data%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20currency%20notes%20it%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20no%20data%20response%20by%20the%20regulator%20is%20bizarre%2C%20given%20the%20fact%20that%20it%20gave%20approval%20to%20make%20CBDC%20transactions%20on%20UPI%20network.%20If%20such%20a%20decision%20was%20indeed%20taken%20without%20necessary%20data%2C%20the%20regulatory%20capability%20is%20seriously%20questionable.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20RBI%20deputy%20governor%2C%20though%2C%20is%20open%20to%20spilling%20some%20numbers%20for%20industry%20%E2%80%93%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.financialexpress.com%2Fbusiness%2Fbanking-finance-seeing-15000-retail-cbdc-transaction-per-day-rbi-deputy-governor-t-rabi-sankar-3243954%2F%5C%22%3Ehad%20said%2015%2C000%20transactions%20happen%20daily%3C%2Fa%3E%20through%20CBDC.%20CBDC%20pilot%20is%20run%20on%20a%20blockchain%20and%20that%20the%20RBI%20through%20NPCI%20has%20access%20to%20detailed%20data%20is%20the%20logical%20expectation.%20The%20only%20reason%2C%20then%2C%20for%20citing%20it%20has%20no%20data%20is%20that%20this%20is%20the%20default%20response%20mode%20and%20allergy%20to%20transparency%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20RTI%20queries.%20This%20lack%20of%20transparency%20%E2%80%93%20especially%20on%20crucial%20matters%20such%20as%20money%20supply%2Fnew%20digital%20currency%20%E2%80%93%20fails%20not%20just%20at%20democratic%20accountability%20levels%2C%20but%20also%20what%20the%20market%20expects.%20Cryptocurrencies%2C%20which%20are%20often%20criticised%20for%20their%20volatility%2C%20publish%20the%20entire%20transaction%20log%20publicly%2C%20making%20them%20more%20transparent%20than%20some%20centralised%20digital%20money%20systems.%20A%20Moody%E2%80%99s%20thumbs%20down%20on%20the%20rupee%20(even%20on%20CBDC)%20will%20be%20far%20more%20costly%20economically%20than%20the%20one%20on%20Aadhaar%2C%20and%20the%20effects%20of%20that%20will%20be%20on%20every%20person%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERegulators%20are%20the%20new%20power%20centres%20and%20regulatory%20accountability%20both%20via%20parliament%20and%20civil%20society%20is%20needed%20to%20prevent%20seemingly%20small%2C%20unknown%20excesses%20that%20have%20large%2C%20irreversible%20damages%20to%20society%20for%20the%20profits%20of%20a%20few.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESrikanth%20Lakshmanan%20is%20part%20of%20CashlessConsumer%2C%20a%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Econsumer%20collective%20working%20on%20digital%20payments%20with%20a%20goal%20of%20moving%20towards%20a%20fair%20cashless%20society%20with%20equitable%20rights.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696244882000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F02163630%2Faakash-dhage-KrpOwO4AIwM-unsplash.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fthe-need-for-regulatory-transparency-and-accountability-around-digital-money%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Systems%20are%20being%20made%20more%20opaque%20than%20ever%20and%20governments%20are%20insulated%20by%20regulators%20who%20hide%20behind%20technology.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fthe-need-for-regulatory-transparency-and-accountability-around-digital-money%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bangladesh%20Records%201%2C000%20Deaths%20in%20Worst-Ever%20Dengue%20Outbreak%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F02152430%2F66791415_1004.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EBangladesh%C2%A0is%20reeling%20from%20the%20worst-ever%20outbreak%20of%20dengue%20this%20year%20which%20has%20claimed%20more%20than%201%2C000%20lives%20since%20the%20start%20of%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20death%20toll%20due%20to%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Ftop-10-most-dangerous-viruses-in-the-world%2Fa-17846283%5C%22%3Eendemic%20disease%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0has%20seen%20a%20staggering%20rise%20this%20year%20when%20compared%20to%20last%20year%E2%80%99s%20281%20deaths.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EData%20shared%20by%20government%20health%20officials%20on%20Sunday%20showed%20that%201%2C006%20people%20have%20died%20since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20year%2C%20of%20which%2017%20were%20reported%20in%20the%20last%2024%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20deaths%20reported%20this%20year%2C%20112%20were%20of%20children%20aged%2015%20and%20under%2C%20including%20infants%2C%20according%20to%20the%20official%20data%20provided%20by%20Directorate%20General%20of%20Health%20Services.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20country%E2%80%99s%20current%20dengue%20caseload%20stands%20at%20more%20than%20200%2C000%20confirmed%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20health%20agency%E2%80%99s%20former%20director%20Be-Nazir%2