the%20view%20put%20forth%20by%20Sengupta%20%E2%80%93%20who%20is%20the%20director%2C%20Vidhi%20Centre%20for%20Legal%20Policy%20%E2%80%93%20and%20the%20arguments%20on%20which%20it%20is%20based%2C%20in%20a%20thrilling%2045-minute%20interview.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWith%20minor%20edits%20for%20style%2C%20this%20is%20the%20full%20text%20of%20their%20conversation.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKaran%20Thapar%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%C2%A0Hello%2C%20and%20welcome%20to%20a%20special%20interview%20for%20%3Ci%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fi%3E.%20A%20recently%20published%20book%20argues%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20constitution%20is%20colonial.%20It%E2%80%99s%20called%20%3Ci%3EThe%20Colonial%20Constitution%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20and%20it%20raises%20a%20fundamental%20question%3A%20is%20the%20book%20right%20and%20is%20our%20constitution%20really%20colonial%2C%20or%20is%20that%20a%20mistaken%20view%3F%20Joining%20me%20now%20to%20answer%20that%20question%20is%20the%20author%20himself%2C%20the%20research%20director%20of%20the%20Vidhi%20Center%20for%20Legal%20Policy%2C%20Arghya%20Sengupta.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EArghya%20Sengupta%2C%20I%20want%20to%20focus%20this%20interview%20on%20your%20belief%20that%20the%20Indian%20constitution%20is%20colonial%2C%20and%20if%20I%E2%80%99ve%20understood%20your%20book%20correctly%20you%20have%20two%20broad%20arguments%20for%20saying%20so.%20Let%E2%80%99s%20go%20through%20them%20one%20by%20one.%20To%20begin%20with%2C%20you%20write%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20constitution%20of%20India%20is%20a%20colonial%20document.%20It%E2%80%99s%20colonial%20for%20the%20simple%20factual%20reason%20that%20it%20is%20heavily%20borrowed%20from%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20Act%201935%2C%20a%20fact%20that%20has%20been%20widely%20glossed%20over%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20true%2C%20but%20only%20in%20the%20sense%20that%20that%E2%80%99s%20the%20broad%20outline%20structure%2C%20and%20you%20can%20see%20that%20when%20you%20go%20on%20in%20your%20book%20to%20say%20%E2%