ree%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Forest%20Research%20Institute%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20is%20currently%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F252429%2Fkashmir-farmers-earns-lakhs-lavender-harvest-cultivation-maize-earnings-success-story-farming-cash-crop-jammu%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egeotagging%20%3Cem%3Echinars%3C%2Fem%3E%20across%20the%20valley%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20know%20their%20number%20as%20well%20as%20their%20health.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20the%20institute%20has%20geotagged%20as%20many%20as%2018%2C000%20of%20these%20trees%20across%20the%20valley%20and%20the%20remaining%2010%2C000%20are%20still%20under%20census.%20Officials%20at%20the%20institute%20claim%20that%20the%20major%20proportion%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Echinars%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20are%20accounted%20for%20are%20diseased%20and%20require%20immediate%20conservation%20efforts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20conduct%20an%20analysis%20of%20every%20%3Cem%3Echinar%20%3C%2Fem%3Etree%20by%20looking%20at%2025%20characteristics%20like%20age%2C%20health%2C%20height%2C%20width%2C%20how%20susceptible%20they%20are%20to%20diseases%2C%20and%20which%20tree%20needs%20aid.%20After%20covering%20Kashmir%2C%20we%20will%20move%20to%20Chenab%20valley%20in%20Jammu%20to%20geotag%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Echinars%3C%2Fem%3E.%20So%20far%20we%20have%20come%20to%20the%20conclusion%20that%20the%20majority%20of%20these%20trees%20in%20the%20valley%20are%20diseased%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Syed%20Tariq%2C%20researcher%20and%20coordinator%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Echinar%3C%2Fem%3E%20census%20project%20of%20the%20institute%2C%20saying%20that%20they%20have%20also%20created%20a%20record%20form%20to%20catalogue%20each%20tree.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20institute%20is%20now%20proposing%20to%20create%20an%20online%20database%20of%20%3Cem%3Echinar%3C%2Fem%3E%20trees%2C%20they%20are%20also%20taking%20various%20revival%20measures%20%E