left%20behind%20as%20residue.%20Being%20in%20the%20pharmaceutical%20field%2C%20I%20came%20across%20Brazilian%20resin%20supplier%20which%20innovated%20sugarcane%20EVA%20(ethylene%20vinyl%20acetate)%20copolymer%20derived%20from%20sugarcane%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Parth.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIntrigued%20to%20utilise%20the%20innovative%20carbon-negative%20material%2C%20Parth%20collaborated%20with%20the%20company%20to%20use%20sugarcane%20EVA%20to%20make%20the%20shoes%E2%80%99%20outsoles%20soft%20and%20comfortable.%20Other%20than%20this%2C%20they%20incorporated%20renewable%20and%20recyclable%20materials%20like%20merino%20wool%20and%20plastic%20water%20bottles%20to%203D-knit%20the%20shoes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EExplaining%20how%20the%20shoes%20are%20made%20from%20recycled%20plastic%20bottles%2C%20Parth%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFirst%2C%20we%20make%20pallets%20from%20plastic%20bottles%20which%20are%20then%20melted%20into%20yarn.%20We%20then%20blend%20merino%20wool%20into%20it%20to%20make%20propitiatory%20threads.%20So%2C%20while%20the%20outsoles%20made%20from%20sugarcane%20EVA%20provide%20durability%20and%20flexibility%20to%20the%20shoe%2C%20yarns%20made%20from%20single-use%20plastic%20bottles%20and%20merino%20wool%20with%20its%20natural%20antibacterial%20properties%20provide%20comfort%20for%20long-day%20use.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FReroute-1695904332.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Interestingly%2C%20the%20duo%20recycles%2011%20plastic%20bottles%20to%20knit%20a%20pair%20of%20shoes.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FReroute-1695904332.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FReroute-1695904332-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FReroute-1695904332-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FReroute-1695904332-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FReroute-1695904332-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-331143%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EInterestingly%2C%20the%20duo%20recycles%2011%20plastic%20bottles%20to%20knit%20a%20pair%20of%20shoes.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3ENeha%20Parekh%2C%20who%20has%20been%20using%20these%20shoes%20for%20almost%20four%20months%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%2C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20part%20of%20my%20corporate%20job%2C%20I%20have%20to%20drive%20and%20stand%20for%20long%20hours.%20The%20shoes%20I%20would%20wear%20were%20not%20comfortable%20and%20made%20my%20feet%20sweaty.%20I%20was%20trying%20to%20find%20some%20comfortable%20shoes%20or%20flats%20options%20which%20I%20could%20wear%20daily%20with%20minimal%20design.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20first%20wore%20Reroute%20shoes%2C%20I%20did%20not%20feel%20like%20these%20shoes%20are%20made%20from%20plastic.%20They%20are%20very%20comfortable%20to%20wear.%20It%20feels%20like%20a%20feather%20on%20my%20skin.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPriced%20at%20Rs%202%2C999%2C%20these%20shoes%20weigh%20180%20grams.%20Parth%20informs%20that%20between%2095%20and%20110%20grams%20of%20this%20comprise%20sugarcane%20residue.%20Interestingly%2C%20the%20duo%20recycles%2011%20plastic%20bottles%20to%20knit%20a%20pair%20of%20shoes.%20So%20far%2C%20they%20have%20turned%20nearly%2040%2C000%20plastic%20water%20bottles%20into%20Reroute%E2%80%99s%20proprietary%20knits.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETrue%20to%20their%20company%E2%80%99s%20motto%2C%20which%20is%20%E2%80%98Made%20Without%20Regrets%E2%80%99%2C%20Parth%20says%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20father%20would%20tell%20us%20that%20if%20you%20are%20not%20happy%20to%20purchase%20a%20product%20yourself%2C%20you%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20able%20to%20sell%20it.%20We%20remembered%20this%20lesson%20while%20manufacturing%20our%20shoes.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CToday%2C%20we%20make%20our%20products%20without%20any%20regrets%2C%20which%20is%20also%20our%20company%E2%80%99s%20motto.%20We%20aim%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F322167%2Fgreen-sole-helps-underprivileged-kids-by-upcycling-discarded-shoes-donate-old-footwear%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erefurbish%20these%20shoes%20%3C%2Fa%3Eonce%20they%20turn%20old%20and%20donate%20them%20to%20the%20needy%20or%20recycle%20them%20to%20make%20new%20products%2C%20just%20like%20our%20father%20envisioned%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Parth.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESource%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fswachhindia.ndtv.com%2Fswachh-kadam-mumbaikar-recycling-shoes-tackle-problem-waste-7526%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESwachh%20Kadam%3A%20This%20Mumbaikar%20Is%20Recycling%20Shoes%20To%20Tackle%20The%20Problem%20Of%20Waste%3A%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3EPublished%20by%20Anisha%20Bhatia%20for%20NDTV%20on%2015%20May%202017%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%20All%20photos%3A%20Reroute%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695906855000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FReroute-4-1695904826.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D331134%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Surat-based%20siblings%20Parth%20and%20Karishma%20Dalal%20are%20making%20eco-friendly%20shoes%20from%20sugarcane%20residue%20and%20plastic%20bottles.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%