ds%20Ramji.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EISRO%20has%2C%20since%20then%2C%20placed%20thousands%20of%20orders%20for%20rocket%20models%20and%20kits.%20Craftizan%20Engineering%20also%20makes%201%3A2%20scale%20models%20with%20models%2050-75%20feet%20tall.%20Ramji%20has%20made%20models%20of%20all%20of%20ISRO%E2%80%99s%20missions%20from%20Chandrayaan-1%2C%202%2C%203%20to%20Gaganyaan.%20Apart%20from%20ISRO%2C%20they%20design%20rockets%20for%20universities%2C%20schools%20and%20private%20dealers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFrom%20crafting%20at%20his%20home%2C%20he%20now%20has%20a%20team%20of%2050%20people%2C%20including%20designers%20and%20engineers.%20They%20also%20design%20train%20models%20and%20have%20showcased%20them%20at%20the%20Mysuru%20railway%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20built%20a%20wall%20museum%20which%20traces%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F323066%2Fchandrayaan-3-the-history-of-how-india-began-one-of-its-most-significant-space-journeys%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EISRO%E2%80%99s%20history%3C%2Fa%3E.%20While%20some%20private%20universities%20have%20placed%20orders%20for%20this%2C%20we%20want%20it%20to%20be%20placed%20at%20government%20schools.%20The%20Maharashtra%20government%20is%20in%20talks%20to%20place%20these%20wall%20museums%20at%20many%20government%20schools%20in%20the%20state%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%2079-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20are%20currently%20working%20on%20wall%20museums%20at%20Science%20City%2C%20Ahmedabad%2C%20PSG%20college%20of%20engineering%2C%20Coimbatore%20and%20Savitha%20University%2C%20Chennai.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20opportunities%20and%20more%20than%20enough%20work%20today.%20We%20have%20orders%20worth%20Rs%2050%20lakhs%20per%20month%20and%20have%20plans%20of%20expanding.%20Thanks%20to%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20Make%20in%20India%20push%2C%20we%20are%20able%20to%20go%20big%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ramji.%3C%2Fp%3E%