-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fkarya-feature-1-1695819981-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-331051%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20workers%20of%20Karya%20are%20paid%20instantly%20and%20can%20work%20remotely%20using%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20app.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Manu%20Chopra%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20project%20aims%20to%20do%20more%20than%20just%20offer%20respectable%20jobs%2C%20as%20implied%20by%20its%20name.%20It%20also%20strives%20to%20give%20rural%20Indians%20the%20chance%20to%20get%20out%20of%20poverty%20and%20lead%20improved%20lives%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Manu%20Chopra%2C%20the%20co-founder.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EExplaining%20how%20the%20startup%20works%2C%20Manu%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20give%20data%20service%20to%20companies.%20Let%E2%80%99s%20say%20that%20Microsoft%20wants%20to%20build%20some%20AI%20in%20Marathi%20and%20it%20asks%20Karya%20to%20sell%2010%2C000%20hours%20of%20audio%20data%20to%20them.%20We%20would%20break%20this%20huge%20task%20into%20micro%20tasks%20and%20distribute%20them%20among%20people%20in%20rural%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20the%20workers%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20they%20simply%20have%20to%20download%20the%20Karya%20application%20and%20read%20out%20sentences%20written%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F267060%2Fjayanti-kathale-viral-video-quit-job-marathi-cuisine-purnabramha-inspiring%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20in%20Marathi.%20%3C%2Fa%3EWe%20then%20combine%20these%20and%20sell%20it%20to%20the%20company%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20encourage%20the%20workers%2C%20we%20pay%20them%20as%20soon%20as%20they%20come%20with%20the%20work.%20They%20do%20not%20have%20to%20put%20in%20a%20certain%20number%20of%20hours%20of%20work