%20He%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20learning%20to%20be%20a%20student%20who%20is%20open%20to%20new%20opportunities%2C%20values%20questioning%20to%20find%20answers%20through%20teaching%2C%20and%20gains%20valuable%20insights%20from%20working%20with%20students%2C%20enabling%20me%20to%20better%20understand%20their%20learning%20needs.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FUntitled-design-10-1695812845.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kamlesh%20with%20his%20students.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FUntitled-design-10-1695812845.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FUntitled-design-10-1695812845-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FUntitled-design-10-1695812845-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FUntitled-design-10-1695812845-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FUntitled-design-10-1695812845-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-331015%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKamlesh%20with%20his%20students.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Cp%3ESeveral%20students%20from%20NPS%20have%20gone%20on%20to%20get%20admission%20to%20the%20likes%20of%20Ashoka%20University%2C%20FLAME%2C%20Delhi%20University%2C%20Azim%20Premji%20University%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKamlesh%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20will%20be%20the%20position%20of%20students%20from%20NPS%20in%20the%20future%2C%20but%20I%20know%20they%20will%20never%20dominate%20marginalised%20communities%20and%20always%20help%20those%20in%20need.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3C